last_episode_to_air.name: November 6th, 2024
last_episode_to_air.overview: NXT emanates from the former ECW Arena in Philadelphia. Trick Williams & WWE Hall of Famer Bubba Ray Dudley face Ethan Page & Ridge Holland.

name: WWE NXT
overview: Wrestlers will portray heroes or villains as they follow a series of events that build tension and culminate in a wrestling match or series of matches.
tagline: WWE NXT features the next generation of Superstars battling to make an impact.

episodes.name: Feb. 23, 2010
episodes.overview: The dream of many is chased by eight hopeful young men looking for their big break in the inaugural edition of NXT. While seasoned WWE Pros mentor each NXT Rookie during their journey, Daniel Bryan finds himself guided by The Miz into main event action against Chris Jericho. Plus, Michael Tarver is in action and Darren Young takes on David Otunga.

episodes.name: Mar. 02, 2010
episodes.overview: After an impressive battle with Chris Jericho on the previous edition of NXT, Daniel Bryan continues to showcase his abilities by going one-on-one with Y2J's NXT Rookie, Wade Barrett. Matt Hardy mentors Justin Gabriel in a Tag Team Match, as they unite to take on Skip Sheffield and his WWE Pro, William Regal. All this and much more!

episodes.name: Mar. 02, 2010
episodes.overview: As the journey of a lifetime continues, Chris Jericho leads Wade Barrett to the ring for main event action against Matt Hardy's NXT Rookie, Justin Gabriel. Heath Slater looks to earn the respect of Carlito when they meet in singles competition. Plus, Darren Young struggles with CM Punk's tutelage, Daniel Bryan in action, and more!

episodes.name: Mar. 16, 2010
episodes.overview: In the hopes of impressing WWE Pro William Regal, Skip Sheffield goes one-on-one with Wade Barrett in the main event. Daniel Bryan finds himself in a "David and Goliath" situation when he faces off against The Great Khali. After a Tag Team Match against Justin Gabriel & Matt Hardy, CM Punk teaches Darren Young a surprising lesson.

episodes.name: Mar. 23, 2010
episodes.overview: As the WWE Pros prepare to reveal their standings in the coming days, the competition between the eight NXT Rookies intensifies in a pair of Tag Team Matches. First, Heath Slater and Justin Gabriel unite to take on Wade Barrett and Skip Sheffield. Then, the main event sees David Otunga and Darren Young battle Daniel Bryan and Michael Tarver.

episodes.name: Mar. 30, 2010
episodes.overview: Weeks of intense competition lead to a startling moment of truth when all eight NXT Rookies find out exactly where they stand in the eyes of the WWE Pros with the reveal of their first poll to see who is on their way to becoming WWE's next breakout star. Plus, the NXT Rookies compete in an Over the Top Rope Battle Royal to see will host Raw!

episodes.name: Apr. 06, 2010
episodes.overview: As the competition to become WWE's next breakout star heats up, a special contest between the NXT Rookies leaves one winner feeling burned in the main event. Plus, Daniel Bryan meets Darren Young in singles action, Wade Barrett goes one-on-one with David Otunga, and more!

episodes.name: Apr. 13, 2010
episodes.overview: After refusing to blindly accept the teachings of CM Punk on SmackDown, Darren Young is given a chance to earn the forgiveness of his WWE Pro if he can defeat Luke Gallows in the main event. Plus, the NXT Rookies look to prove that they can talk the talk, Wade Barrett battles Christian, and more!

episodes.name: Apr. 20, 2010
episodes.overview: The NXT Rookies face off in a challenge that ends up leaving their world rocked. Heath Slater looks to see if he has what it takes to break down the walls by going one-on-one with Chris Jericho. As Michael Tarver and Skip Sheffield prepare to meet in singles action, CM Punk looks to give his NXT Rookie some competition. All this and more!

episodes.name: Apr. 27, 2010
episodes.overview: It's all about the money on this edition of NXT, as the NXT Rookies show their skills at salesmanship in a new contest. Before taking to the ring for a scheduled bout against Skip Sheffield in the main event, The Miz has a special surprise for his NXT Rookie, Daniel Bryan. Wade Barrett & Chris Jericho unite to take on Heath Slater & Christian.

episodes.name: May 04, 2010
episodes.overview: As the first season of NXT continues, the NXT Rookies find themselves faced with a number of obstacles on their journey. With his recent victory giving him the right to select any opponent of his own choosing, David Otunga decides to challenge R-Truth to singles action in the main event. All this and much more!

episodes.name: May 11, 2010
episodes.overview: The situation for each of the NXT Rookies becomes dire when the WWE Pros reveal their decisions on who will be the first to be eliminated from the competition. While everyone is on the chopping block, David Otunga tries to shake off his detractors by going one-on-one with Justin Gabriel in the main event.

episodes.name: May 18, 2020
episodes.overview: Following his recent elimination alongside Michael Tarver and Skip Sheffield, Daniel Bryan seizes an opportunity to strike back to his most outspoken detractor, Michael Cole. As the remaining five NXT Rookies wait to see whose journey will come to an end next, Heath Slater takes to the battle Justin Gabriel in the main event. All this and more!

episodes.name: May 25, 2010
episodes.overview: With the first season of NXT rapidly coming to a close, the WWE Pros vow that there will be another elimination just a week before the highly anticipated finale. Plus, Wade Barrett takes on Justin Gabriel in the main event, David Otunga and R-Truth take on Christian and Heath Slater, and more!

episodes.name: Jun. 01, 2010: Final
episodes.overview: After weeks of intense competition, the first season of NXT comes to an end with the revelation of who will be WWE's next breakout star. While awaiting the news of whose journey to the main roster will continue, the three remaining NXT Rookies take to the ring as Wade Barrett, Justin Gabriel and David Otunga compete in a Triple Threat Match.

episodes.name: NXT 16
episodes.overview: With the conclusion of the first season of NXT unintentionally giving birth to a band of vigilantes known as The Nexus, a new crop of NXT Rookies begin their journey on the receiving end of a hard lesson from their WWE Pros.

episodes.name: NXT 17
episodes.overview: Following their recent and painful initiation at the hands of their WWE Pros, the new crop of NXT Rookies take to the ring to show the WWE Universe that they have what it takes to continue this incredible journey in trying to become the next breakout star. Plus, in his in-ring debut, Alex Riley faces off against fellow newcomer Kaval.

episodes.name: NXT 18
episodes.overview: While time is of the essence for the NXT Rookies in the shadow of the first WWE Pros Poll, Lucky Cannon finds himself feeling the pressure of the clock when he battles Cody Rhodes in the main event. Plus, Kaval meets Eli Cottonwood in singles action, Titus O'Neil takes on Michael McGillicutty, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 19
episodes.overview: As the NXT Rookies are faced with the first major elimination of the season, Lucky Cannon looks to live up to his name in a special contest. Plus, a huge Six-Man Tag Team Match, Husky Harris takes to the ring to battle MVP, and much more action!

episodes.name: NXT 20
episodes.overview: While the NXT Rookies try to prove that they can talk the talk, Kaval looks to prove that he can walk the walk when he goes one-on-one with United States Champion The Miz. Cody Rhodes and Husky Harris take on Mark Henry and Lucky Cannon in a Tag Team Match main event. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 21
episodes.overview: On a night where the WWE Pros and NXT Rookies meet each other in a Battle Royal main event, Wade Barrett and his Nexus return to their origins to make their presence felt in a big way. Plus, Alex Riley and United States Champion The Miz face Lucky Cannon and Mark Henry in a Tag Team Match, Percy Watson unveils a new segment, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 22
episodes.overview: More obstacles stand in the way of the NXT Rookies on their journey to becoming WWE's next breakout stars. After a confrontation on his VIP Lounge, MVP and Percy Watson take to the ring to battle Cody Rhodes and his NXT Rookie, Husky Harris. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 23
episodes.overview: With the threat of an elimination hanging over each of their heads, the NXT Rookies are given a chance to speak about any topic they choose in under a minute. LayCool leads Kaval to the ring for main event competition against Cody Rhodes' Rookie, Husky Harris. Plus, Percy Watson, Michael McGillicutty, and more in action!

episodes.name: NXT 24
episodes.overview: Before he can fulfill his desire to take on United States Champion The Miz in singles competition, Michael McGillicutty must first defeat Mark Henry's NXT Rookie, Lucky Cannon. Plus, LayCool surprises the NXT Rookies with an unusual challenge, Alex Riley goes one-on-one with Percy Watson, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 25
episodes.overview: As the WWE Pros Poll promises another elimination by the end of the night, the NXT Rookies compete in contest aptly entitled 'Power of the Punch'. Two former allies collide in the main event when United States Champion The Miz goes one-on-one with fellow WWE Pro, John Morrison. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 26
episodes.overview: With only five competitors remaining, the journey of NXT Rookies to becoming WWE's next breakout star becomes a dire situation in the shadow of the impending WWE Pros Poll. In the main event, Alex Riley goes one-on-one with Kofi Kingston. All this and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 27
episodes.overview: As the second season of NXT draws closer to an end, the remaining three NXT Rookies test their knowledge of sports entertainment history when Kaval, Michael McGillicutty, and Alex Riley face off in a special WWE Trivia Challenge. Two WWE Pros clash in the main event, as Cody Rhodes goes one-on-one with MVP. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 28
episodes.overview: While the WWE Universe readies to find out who will become WWE's next breakout star on the finale of NXT's second season, the remaining NXT Rookies compete in a Triple Threat Match main event that sees Kaval battle Michael McGillicutty and Alex Riley. Plus, a look at what's to come in season 3!

episodes.name: NXT 29
episodes.overview: The third of season of NXT takes on a new identity as six young women begin a journey to become WWE's next breakout Diva. After competing in a special Dance Challenge, the NXT Rookies look to showcase their in-ring skills in a pair of exciting matches. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 30
episodes.overview: With a pair of challenges proving that the journey to becoming the next breakout Diva is no laughing matter, the NXT Rookies find themselves in some unusual situations. Plus, Intercontinental Champion Dolph Ziggler and Kaitlyn take on AJ and Primo in a Mixed Tag Team Match, Jamie takes on Aksana, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 31
episodes.overview: On a night where the NXT Rookies look to find their place in a pair of special challenges, Kaitlyn unites with LayCool to take on Naomi, Kelly Kelly, and Jamie in a Six-Diva Tag Team Match main event.

episodes.name: NXT 32
episodes.overview: As the first eliminations of the season rapidly approach, tensions amongst the NXT Rookies explode when the second of two challenges leaves the would-be Divas with some hurt feelings.

episodes.name: NXT 33
episodes.overview: While the preparing for the first elimination on their journey to becoming WWE's next breakout Diva, the NXT Rookies look to literally grab the bull by the horns with their next challenges. Plus, Kaitlyn looks to settle a score with Vickie Guerrero in the main event!

episodes.name: NXT 34
episodes.overview: In the midst of their journey to WWE's main roster, the NXT Rookies continue to prove their durability in a pair of entertaining challenges. Plus, AJ goes one-on-one with Aksana in the main event, Naomi takes on Alicia Fox, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 35
episodes.overview: On a night where the NXT Rookies see how low they can go, Kaitlyn's negative perception of WWE Pro Vickie Guerrero leads her into singles action against Maxine. Plus, Kelly Kelly and Naomi unite to take on The Bella Twins in the main event!

episodes.name: NXT 36
episodes.overview: In the midst of the Halloween season, the NXT Rookies look to celebrate the holiday with a pair of special contests modeled after the spookiest night of the year. Goldust and Aksana united to take on Ted DiBiase and Maryse in a Mixed Tag Team Match main event. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 37
episodes.overview: Despite facing an upcoming elimination along with her fellow NXT Rookies, Aksana takes a huge leap of faith by taking to the ring in order to marry Goldust. Plus, a pair of unique contests, Kelly Kelly battles Alicia Fox, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 38
episodes.overview: After revealing her true intentions in her 'marriage' to Goldust, Aksana takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Naomi in the main event. Plus, a pair of contests that test knowledge and strength, AJ takes on Nikki Bella, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 39
episodes.overview: With the journey to becoming WWE's next breakout Diva winding down, the NXT Rookies wait with anticipation to see which one of them will be up next for elimination. Plus, Kaitlyn meets Naomi in singles action, AJ battles Aksana, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 40
episodes.overview: As the season finale of NXT draws closer, the NXT Rookies prepare for the next elimination by participating in some unique challenges. Plus, Naomi takes to the ring to go one-on-one with AJ!

episodes.name: NXT 41
episodes.overview: On the season finale of NXT, the dream of six NXT Rookies becomes a reality for one lucky Diva as the winner of season 3 is revealed to the WWE Universe. While Naomi and Kaitlyn take to the ring compete against each other in one final bout, the previously eliminated competitors meet in a Six-Diva Tag Team Match. Plus, a sneak peak of season 4!

episodes.name: NXT 42
episodes.overview: Season 4 of NXT kicks off with the introduction of a brand new crop of NXT Rookies looking to start their journey to becoming WWE's next breakout star. WWE Pros and NXT Rookies unite for main event action when Alberto Del Rio and Conor O'Brian take on United States Champion Daniel Bryan and Derrick Bateman in a Tag Team Match!

episodes.name: NXT 43
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, WWE Pro Alberto Del Rio takes to the ring to go one-on-one with NXT Rookie Derrick Bateman in the main event. Plus, several obstacles appear on the road to WWE's main roster, Brodus Clay and Ted DiBiase take on Chris Masters and Byron Saxton, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 44
episodes.overview: On a night where the NXT Rookies find themselves in the hot seat, Ted DiBiase partners with Brodus Clay and Maryse to take on the trio of Chris Masters, Byron Saxton, and Natalya in the main event. Plus, a Wheel Barrow Challenge, Johnny Curtis in action, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 45
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, a special Talent Show leads to an all out brawl between this season's crop of NXT Rookies. Plus, Derrick Bateman takes to the ring to meet Conor O'Brian in singles action, Ted DiBiase battles Byron Saxton, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 46
episodes.overview: With an elimination hanging over their heads, the NXT Rookies find out exactly what championship they will be competing for if they come out on top this season. The WWE Pros compete in a Battle Royal for the right to trade their NXT Rookie. Plus, a Battle of the Mic Challenge, Brodus Clay meets Johnny Curtis in the main event, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 47
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, R-Truth leads Johnny Curtis to the ring for a main event battle with Ted DiBiase. Plus, Derrick Bateman and Daniel Bryan go out on a double date with The Bella Twins, Conor O'Brian faces off against Byron Saxton, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 48
episodes.overview: While waiting for news of the season's next elimination, the NXT Rookies look to see how well they know their WWE Pros in another special challenge. Plus, Ricardo Rodriguez takes on Conor O'Brian in the main event, Derrick Bateman and United States Champion Daniel Bryan battle Brodus Clay and Ted DiBiase, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 49
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, a Fatal 4-Way Elimination Match sees Brodus Clay battle Johnny Curtis, Byron Saxton, and Derrick Bateman in the main event. Plus, the NXT Rookies test their knowledge against Howard Finkel, Ted DiBiase takes on United States Champion Daniel Bryan, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 50
episodes.overview: After getting his bell rung in an Arm-Wrestling Challenge, Johnny Curtis takes to the ring to partner with R-Truth against Derrick Bateman and United States Champion Daniel Bryan in Tag Team Match main event. The student battles the mentor when Ted DiBiase goes one-on-one with Brodus Clay. All this and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 51
episodes.overview: While the contestants battle for immunity from the upcoming elimination, Brodus Clay takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Johnny Curtis in the main event. Byron Saxton faces off against Derrick Bateman in singles competition. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 52
episodes.overview: With the season finale of NXT just weeks away, a WWE Pro battles against his NXT Rookie as United States Champion Daniel Bryan goes one-on-one with Derrick Bateman in the main event. Plus, a pair of special challenges, Brodus Clay takes on R-Truth, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 53
episodes.overview: As the season finale approaches, the absence of their WWE Pros leaves NXT Rookies Brodus Clay, Derrick Bateman, and Johnny Curtis to fend for themselves in shadow of elimination. After moving through obstacles in their paths, all three men compete in a Triple Threat Match main event. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 54
episodes.overview: With only Johnny Curtis and Brodus Clay remaining on the season finale of NXT, both men go head-to-head in singles action before finding out whose journey to WWE will continue. Plus, previously eliminated NXT Rookies Byron Saxton, Derrick Bateman, Conor O'Brian, and Jacob Novak return for a Tag Team Match!

episodes.name: NXT 55
episodes.overview: Redemption is the prize for the competitors of the 5th season of NXT, as Derrick Bateman, Darren Young, Titus O'Neil, Conor O'Brian, Lucky Cannon, Byron Saxton, and Jacob Novak return to fulfill the journey they began on past seasons.

episodes.name: NXT 56
episodes.overview: On a night where the contestants of NXT look to test both their physical and verbal strengths in a pair of challenges, Tyson Kidd and Lucky Cannon team up to take on Yoshi Tatsu and Byron Saxton in a Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Conor O'Brian goes one-on-one with Darren Young!

episodes.name: NXT 57
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Byron Saxton takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Lucky Cannon in the main event. Plus, a Battle of the Mic Challenge, Darren Young faces off against Titus O'Neil in singles action, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 58
episodes.overview: After the contestants battle for redemption points in a special strength challenge, Titus O'Neil partners with Byron Saxton and Conor O'Brian to take on Lucky Cannon, Jacob Novak, and Darren Young in a Six-Man Tag Team Match main event. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 59
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Yoshi Tatsu's attempts to get Maryse to go out with him earn him the wrath of Ted DiBiase that leads to them facing off in the main event. Plus, Jacob Novak in action, Titus O'Neil battles Darren Young, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 60
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Lucky Cannon takes to the ring to battle Yoshi Tatsu in the main event. Plus, a Power of the Punch Challenge, Titus O'Neil goes one-on-one with Darren Young, and much more action!

episodes.name: NXT 61
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Lucky Cannon and Tyson Kidd face off against Yoshi Tatsu and Byron Saxton in a Tag Team Match main event. While continuing to call out William Regal, Jacob Novak takes to the ring to battle Conor O'Brian in singles action. All this and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 62
episodes.overview: After a challenge to see how well they know their WWE Pros, this season's crop of NXT Rookies look to show their abilities in several exciting matches, including Byron Saxton taking on Lucky Cannon in the main event. Plus, JTG and Jacob Novak team up, Darren Young battles Titus O'Neil, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 63
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, William Regal gets more than expected when he looks to teach Jacob Novak a lesson in a main event battle. Plus, Conor O'Brian competes in singles action, Darren Young goes one-on-one with Chavo Guerrero, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 64
episodes.overview: After weeks of repeated enduring taunts, William Regal takes to the ring to teach Jacob Novak a lesson in the main event. Plus, a Grab the Flag Challenge, Conor O'Brian goes one-on-one with Byron Saxton, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 65
episodes.overview: In the shadow of the first elimination of NXT Redemption, JTG takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Vladimir Kozlov in the main event. After Darren Young faces off against Titus O'Neil in singles action, Chavo Guerrero makes an example out of Hornswoggle. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 66
episodes.overview: On this edition NXT Redemption, Hornswoggle looks to get a measure of revenge on Chavo Guerrero when Titus O'Neil takes to the ring to battle Darren Young in a No Disqualification Match main event. Plus, JTG in action, Byron Saxton makes a drastic decision. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 67
episodes.overview: With another elimination standing in the way of one man's journey to WWE, the remaining NXT Rookies take to the ring for an exciting Tag Team Turmoil Match main event in which Tyson Kidd & Lucky Cannon battle the teams of Darren Young & Chavo Guerrero, Titus O'Neil & Hornswoggle, Yoshi Tatsu & Byron Saxton, and Conor O'Brian & Vladimir Kozlov!

episodes.name: NXT 68
episodes.overview: When JTG invites Yoshi Tatsu to a special edition of Straight Outta Brooklyn, a confrontation between them leads both men to face each other in singles action. Plus, Titus O'Neil goes one-on-one with Lucky Cannon in the main event, Hornswoggle uses his head, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 69
episodes.overview: While facing another big elimination on this edition of NXT Redemption, the contestants take to the ring to compete in a Talk the Talk Challenge. Plus, Lucky Cannon goes one-on-one with Titus O'Neil in the main event, Darren Young faces Yoshi Tatsu, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 70
episodes.overview: After Hornswoggle offers Maryse a gift from the heart, Zack Ryder picks a fight with Titus O'Neil that leads to them meeting each other in the main event. Plus, Yoshi Tatsu, Chavo Guerrero, and more compete in a Six-Man Tag Team Match!

episodes.name: NXT 71
episodes.overview: With a lack of redemption points putting him at risk for almost certain elimination, Conor O'Brian takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Darren Young. Plus, Titus O'Neil faces off against JTG in the main event, Tyson Kidd battles Yoshi Tatsu, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 72
episodes.overview: Long before the days of The Prime Time Players, Darren Young and Titus O'Neil find themselves uniting for action when they take on Derrick Bateman and Daniel Bryan in a Tag Team Match main event. Plus, a Talk the Talk Challenge, Tyson Kidd goes one-on-one with Yoshi Tatsu, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 73
episodes.overview: After a hostile exchange of words, NXT Rookies Titus O'Neil, Derrick Bateman, and Darren Young face each other in a Triple Threat Elimination Match. Plus, Hornswoggle receives a gift from a secret admirer, Tyson Kidd goes one-on-one with Yoshi Tatsu, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 74
episodes.overview: Following a unique demonstration that escalates tensions, Titus O'Neil prepares for action as he takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Darren Young in the main event. Plus, JTG in action, Hornswoggle confronts Maryse about his special gift, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 75
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Yoshi Tatsu and Tyson Kidd take to new heights when they meet in a Necklace on a Pole Match in the main event. Plus, Hornswoggle discovers his secret admirer, Titus O'Neil goes one-on-one with Derrick Bateman, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 76
episodes.overview: The alliance of Derrick Bateman and Darren Young shocks the WWE Universe when they personally select a partner for Titus O'Neil to help him take on both men in the main event. Plus, JTG meets Vladimir Kozlov in singles action, Tyson Kidd continues his crusade against Yoshi Tatsu, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 77
episodes.overview: After taking exception to Matt Striker's honesty, Darren Young challenges Striker to face him in singles action. Plus, Tyson Kidd looks to teach Justin Gabriel a lesson, Derrick Bateman goes one-on-one with Titus O'Neil in the main event, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 78
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Maxine arrives to make a huge statement at the expense of AJ before escorting Derrick Bateman to the ring for main event competition against Titus O'Neil. Plus, Tyson Kidd in action, Matt Striker faces Darren Young, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 79
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Darren Young looks to take out all his frustrations on an unexpecting Matt Striker. Plus, AJ battles Maxine in the main event, Tyson Kidd goes one-on-one with Trent Barreta, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 80
episodes.overview: On a very special edition of NXT, Matt Striker takes the WWE Universe on a journey to catch up on the current careers of the WWE Superstars and Divas who graduated from NXT, including Wade Barrett, Alex Riley, and many more!

episodes.name: NXT 81
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, William Regal looks to make Darren Young pay for his lack of respect by facing him one-on-one in the main event. Plus, Titus O'Neil and AJ take on Maxine and Derrick Bateman in a Mixed Tag Team Match, Tyson Kidd battles Yoshi Tatsu, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 82
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, an altercation early in the night leads to JTG and Darren Young teaming up to take on William Regal and Matt Striker in the main event. Plus, Derrick Bateman in action, AJ battles Maxine, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 83
episodes.overview: After interrupting Titus O'Neil's appearance on Percy Watson's Showtime, JTG and Darren Young find themselves battling both men in a Tag Team Match main event. Plus, AJ in action, Derrick Bateman goes one-on-one with Yoshi Tatsu, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 84
episodes.overview: Weeks of making their presence felt in the Tag Team Division at the expense of JTG and Darren Young leads The Usos to take to the ring to battle their foes in a Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Jinder Mahal meets Yoshi Tatsu in singles action, Percy Watson takes on Tyson Kidd, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 85
episodes.overview: In response to the perceived anarchy taking place in NXT, Tyler Reks and Curt Hawkins set up a Tag Team Match against The Usos in the main event. Daniel Bryan takes to the ring to battle his former Nexus ally, Heath Slater. Plus, Derrick Bateman, JTG, and more in action!

episodes.name: NXT 86
episodes.overview: After a hilarious exchange of words, Percy Watson takes to the ring to settle a score with Derrick Bateman in the main event. Plus, The Usos battle Curt Hawkins and Tyler Reks in a Tag Team Match, AJ goes one-on-one with Maxine, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 87
episodes.overview: Following a controversial Capture the Flag Challenge, Titus O'Neil and Percy Watson gear up to take on Derrick Bateman and a partner of his choosing in a Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Tyler Reks in action, Maxine goes one-on-one with Kaitlyn, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 88
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, a Talk the Talk Challenge between Titus O'Neil and Derrick Bateman leads to both men facing off against each other in the main event. Plus, Jey Uso meets Tyson Kidd in singles action, Kaitlyn battles Tamina Snuka, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 89
episodes.overview: An insulted Derrick Bateman and Maxine look for revenge by partnering with JTG to take on Titus O'Neil, Percy Watson, and AJ in a special Intergender Six-Person Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Kaitlyn, The Usos, and many more in action!

episodes.name: NXT 90
episodes.overview: When tensions arise between Derrick Bateman and Johnny Curtis over Maxine's past romantic encounters, Matt Striker seizes an opportunity by having both men unite to take on Titus O'Neil and Percy Watson in a Tag Team Match main event. Plus, JTG in action, Trent Barreta battles Tyson Kidd, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 91
episodes.overview: Fresh off his recent suspension, Tyler Reks returns to action by going one-on-one with Titus O'Neil in the main event. Plus, Percy Watson takes to the ring to battle Derrick Bateman in singles action, Johnny Curtis continues to pursue Maxine, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 92
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Darren Young takes to the ring to partner with Tyler Reks in a Tag Team Match main event against Percy Watson and Titus O'Neil. Plus, JTG competes in singles action, Johnny Curtis battles Yoshi Tatsu, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 93
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, a Triple Threat Match main event sees Derrick Bateman, Darren Young, and Titus O'Neil battle for an opportunity to compete on SmackDown. Plus, Percy Watson in action, Johnny Curtis and Tyson Kidd meet Yoshi Tatsu and Trent Barreta in a Tag Team Match, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 94
episodes.overview: When the love triangle between Derrick Bateman, Maxine, and Johnny Curtis becomes a family affair, Bateman and Curtis look to resolve their differences in the main event. Plus, The Usos, Titus O'Neil, and many more take to the ring for action!

episodes.name: NXT 95
episodes.overview: After Derrick Bateman incites violence between Johnny Curtis and Percy Watson on a brand new edition of Showtime, Curtis and Watson find themselves facing off against each other in the main event. A heated exchange between Titus O'Neil and Darren Young leads to a brawl between both men. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 96
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Derrick Bateman proves a less than reliable tag team partner when he and Johnny Curtis face off against The Usos. Plus, Titus O'Neil takes to the ring to battle JTG in the main event, Tyson Kidd faces Percy Watson, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 97
episodes.overview: When Justin Gabriel returns to his origins on an all new edition of NXT Redemption, he immediately finds himself going one-on-one with his former Nexus ally, Heath Slater. Amidst their sordid love triangle with Maxine, Johnny Curtis and Derrick Bateman take to the ring to battle each other in the main event.

episodes.name: NXT 98
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, an altercation between Michael McGillicutty and Alex Riley leads Matt Striker to have them face each other in singles action. Plus, Derrick Bateman goes one-on-one with Darren Young in the main event, Trent Barreta takes on Curt Hawkins, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 99
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Johnny Curtis takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Alex Riley in the main event. Tensions between Titus O'Neil and Darren Young reach a boiling point. Plus, The Usos take on JTG and Tyson Kidd in a Tag Team Match, Maxine picks a fight with Alicia Fox, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 100
episodes.overview: Wedding bells are in the air on the special 100th episode of NXT, as Maxine prepares to marry the unusual Johnny Curtis. Titus O'Neil displays a new demeanor after taking to the ring to battle Darren Young in a No Disqualification Match. All this and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 101
episodes.overview: Titus O'Neil's recent change in attitude leads to him to compete in main event action against his former ally, Percy Watson. Plus, The Usos battle Curt Hawkins and Tyler Reks in a Tag Team Match, Maxine gets some payback on Johnny Curtis, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 102
episodes.overview: When Darren Young and Titus O'Neil set aside their differences out of mutual respect of each other, both men find themselves teaming up to take on Percy Watson and Alex Riley in the main event. Johnny Curtis picks the worst time to ask Maxine's forgiveness. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 103
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, The Usos take to the ring to battle the devious duo of Curt Hawkins and Tyler Reks in a Tag Team Match main event. After meeting Trent Barreta in singles action, Tyson Kidd makes an unexpected offer to his opponent. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 104
episodes.overview: When William Regal takes charge on this edition of NXT Redemption, Tyler Reks finds himself banned from ringside during a match between Curt Hawkins and Tyson Kidd. Plus, Heath Slater and Johnny Curtis take on Justin Gabriel and Derrick Bateman in the main event, Yoshi Tatsu in action, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 105
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Darren Young gets a ringside seat to witness Titus O'Neil go one-on-one with Alex Riley in the main event. After an exchange of words, Tyson Kidd and Tyler Reks meet each other in singles action. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 106
episodes.overview: Despite his passion for WWE, Matt Striker takes to the ring to announce a new General Manager of NXT. After staging a shocking intervention for Derrick Bateman, Kaitlyn prepares to battle a vengeful Maxine in the main event. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 107
episodes.overview: On a night where every match is determine by William Regal, Titus O'Neil takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Percy Watson in the main event. Plus, Johnny Curtis meets Yoshi Tatsu in singles action, Darren Young battles Jey Uso, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 108
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Johnny Curtis and Maxine unite to take on Derrick Bateman and Kaitlyn in a Mixed Tag Team Match main event. The tensions between Michael McGillicutty and Tyson Kidd explode in a violent confrontation. All this and much more action!

episodes.name: NXT 109
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Johnny Curtis' plans to subdue Matt Striker take an unexpected turn. Tyson Kidd takes to the ring to battle Michael McGillicutty in the main event. Plus, Tyler Reks, Justin Gabriel, and many more in action!

episodes.name: NXT 110
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Titus O'Neil takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Jey Uso in the main event. Plus, Matt Striker's whereabouts remain a mystery, Hunio takes on Derrick Bateman in singles action, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 111
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, those responsible for Matt Striker's kidnapping are revealed after Johnny Curtis and Maxine go on a search for the perpetrators. Derrick Bateman takes to the ring to battle Michael McGillicutty in the main event. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 112
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Michael McGillicutty takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Tyson Kidd in the main event. Curt Hawkins and Tyler Reks' plan to hold Matt Striker hostage backfires. All this and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 113
episodes.overview: After being caught red handed for Matt Stiker's kidnapping, Curt Hawkins and Tyler Reks find themselves battling against each other for their jobs in the main event. Plus, Kaitlyn in action, Percy Watson goes one-on-one with Johnny Curtis, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 114
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, things take an unexpected turn when Johnny Curtis and Michael McGillicutty take to the ring to battle Tyson Kidd and Percy Watson in the main event. After making a violent statement, JTG finds himself going one-on-one with Derrick Bateman. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 115
episodes.overview: After accepting a challenge with Tyson Kidd to take on Johnny Curtis and JTG in a Tag Team Match, Alex Riley suffers a mysterious attack. In the main event, Percy Watson goes one-on-one with Michael McGillicutty. All this and more on this edition of NXT Redemption!

episodes.name: NXT 116
episodes.overview: In a light of the recent and suspicious attack of Alex Riley, William Regal takes measures to prevent further incidents from taking place. Plus, Michael McGillicutty and Johnny Curtis take on Percy Watson and Tyson Kidd in the main event, JTG battles Yoshi Tatsu, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 117
episodes.overview: Michael McGillicutty takes to the ring to battle Derrick Bateman and Tyson Kidd in a Triple Threat Match main event. Plus, Ezekiel Jackson and The Great Khali face Tyler Reks and Curt Hawkins in a Tag Team Match, Johnny Curtis goes one-on-one with Percy Watson, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 118
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Johnny Curtis and Drew McIntyre are in for an enormous challenge when they take on The Great Khali and Ezekiel Jackson in a Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Jinder Mahal in action, Alicia Fox takes on Maxine, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 119
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT Redemption, Justin Gabriel partners with Percy Watson and Derrick Bateman to take on the trio of Johnny Curtis, Michael McGillicutty, and JTG in a Six-Man Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Kaitlyn, The Usos, and more are in action!

episodes.name: NXT 120
episodes.overview: Johnny Curtis unites with Heath Slater to take on the innovative duo of Justin Gabriel and Tyson Kidd in a memorable Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Tyler Reks faces off against Jey Uso in singles action, Percy Watson goes one-on-one with JTG, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 121
episodes.overview: On what would be the final edition of NXT Redemption, Michael McGillicutty partners with Johnny Curtis to take on The Usos in a Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Kaitlyn faces Natalya in singles action, Percy Watson and Derrick Bateman battle Curt Hawkins and Tyler Reks, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 122
episodes.overview: The dream of NXT is realized when Dusty Rhodes is named the brand's Interim General Manager. In the main event, Tyson Kidd goes one-on-one with Michael McGillicutty. Plus, Damien Sandow chooses not to participate in what he feels is beneath him, Bo Dallas makes his debut in a match against Rick Victor, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 123
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Seth Rollins looks to prove that the future is now when he takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Jiro. With the beautiful Aksana in his corner, Antonio Cesaro prepares for action against Dante Dash. Plus, Johnny Curtis faces Derrick Bateman in the main event, Leo Kruger battles Aiden English, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 124
episodes.overview: After trying to make an example out of Seth Rollins, Hunico and Camacho partner with Michael McGillicutty to take on Rollins, Tyson Kidd, and Bo Dallas in a Six-Man Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Kassius Ohno clashes with Mike Dalton in singles action, Derrick Bateman goes one-on-one with Jinder Mahal, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 125
episodes.overview: The world of NXT gets a lot stranger when Bray Wyatt arrives to go one-on-one with Aiden English. Tyson Kidd takes to the ring to battle Camacho in an incredible contest. Plus, The Usos take on The Prime Time Players in the main event, a brawl breaks out between Leo Kruger and Richie Steamboat, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 126
episodes.overview: Two former Nexus members clash in the main event, as Heath Slater takes to the ring to go one-on-one with former ally, Justin Gabriel. The recent problems between Leo Kruger and Richie Steamboat lead to in-ring confrontation. Plus, Raquel Diaz makes her NXT debut, Jinder Mahal takes on 'Showtime' Percy Watson, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 127
episodes.overview: WWE's Drew McIntyre travels to NXT to go one-on-one with the incomparable Seth Rollins in the main event. Bo Dallas partners with Derrick Bateman to take on Johnny Curtis and Michael McGillicutty in a Tag Team Match. Plus, Kassius Ohno vows to bring an element of danger to NXT, Sofia Cortez battles Natalya, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 128
episodes.overview: In an effort to give the Superstars of NXT something to dream for, Interim General Manager Dusty Rhodes announces that Seth Rollins, Bo Dallas, Leo Kruger, and many more will compete in a Gold Rush Tournament to crown the first ever NXT Champion. Plus, Big E Langston arrives, Raquel Diaz takes on Audrey Marie, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 129
episodes.overview: The allure of gold and glory leads Bo Dallas, Justin Gabriel, and more to perform to the best of their abilities in the Gold Rush Tournament to crown the first ever NXT Champion. Plus, Kassius Ohno meets CJ Parker in singles action, Paige teams with Tamina Snuka to take on Caylee Turner and Kaitlyn, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 130
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, the Semi-Finals of the Gold Rush Tournament to crown the first ever NXT Champion sees Seth Rollins, Richie Steamboat, and more continue their quest for gold and glory. Plus, The Usos take on The Ascension in a Tag Team Match, Heath Slater issues an open challenge, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 131
episodes.overview: As the conclusion of the Gold Rush Tournament draws near, Seth Rollins and Jinder Mahal meet for a face-to-face confrontation before their upcoming battle for the NXT Championship. In the main event, Michael McGillicutty and Johnny Curtis take on Justin Gabriel and Tyson Kidd. Plus, Antonio Cesaro, Sofia Cortez, and more in action!

episodes.name: NXT 132
episodes.overview: With Seth Rollins and Jinder Mahal set to battle to become the first ever NXT Champion in an unforgettable main event, the WWE Universe gathers to witness how history is made. Plus, Big E Langston looks to continue his success in singles competition, The Usos call out The Ascension for some unfinished business, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 133
episodes.overview: Following his recent victory to become the first ever NXT Champion, Seth Rollins kicks off his title reign by joining Jim Ross for an interview about what's in store for the future. Kassius Ohno shows everyone how dangerous he can be in a match against Richie Steamboat. Plus, Leo Kruger in action, Paige faces Audrey Marie, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 134
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Tyson Kidd takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Michael McGillicutty in the main event. Rick Victor makes his intentions to challenge Seth Rollins for the NXT Championship known. Plus, Big E Langston in action, Damien Sandow takes on Garrett Dylan, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 135
episodes.overview: In an effort to prove that he's worthy of a championship opportunity, Rick Victor takes to the ring to go one-on-one with NXT Champion Seth Rollins in a non-title main event. Kassius Ohno continues to show how dangerous he can be by hosting a Sparring Session. Plus, Johnny Curtis in action, Paige battles Alicia Fox, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 136
episodes.overview: Richie Steamboat has revenge on his mind when he takes to the ring to face Kassius Ohno in the main event. As a result of their recent physical altercation, Bo Dallas and Michael McGillicutty look to resolve their differences in singles action. Ryback battles Aiden English and Francis Remi Dorian in a Handicap Match. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 137
episodes.overview: With his status as Number One Contender earning him a shot at the NXT Championship, Michael McGillicutty takes to the ring to call out the current champion, Seth Rollins. Plus, Tyson Kidd and Justin Gabriel team up to take on The Ascension in the main event, the rivalry between Kassius Ohno and Richie Steamboat continues, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 138
episodes.overview: Before defending the NXT Championship for the first time in a main event battle against Michael McGillicutty, Seth Rollins receives a lesson in respect from WWE Champion CM Punk. Plus, Alicia Fox partners with Kaitlyn to take on Audrey Marie and Paige in a Tag Team Match, Bo Dallas faces Johnny Curtis, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 139
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Richie Steamboat partners with The Usos to take on Kassius Ohno and The Ascension in a huge Six-Man Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Damien Sandow returns to NXT to face off against Brandon Traven in singles action, Alex Riley goes one-on-one with Jinder Mahal, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 140
episodes.overview: Heath Slater takes to the ring to battle NXT Champion Seth Rollins in a non-title main event. Despite not being medically cleared for competition, Richie Steamboat looks to make his presence felt when Kassius Ohno takes on Trent Barreta. Plus, Tyson Kidd takes exception to Antonio Cesaro's patriotism, Paige in action, and more.

episodes.name: NXT 141
episodes.overview: Several Superstars look to stake their claim in the NXT Title picture. Antonio Cesaro defends the United States Championship against Tyson Kidd in the main event. Big E Langston receives a special offer from Vickie Guerrero. Plus, Roman Reigns makes his NXT debut, Leo Kruger faces Xavier Woods, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 142
episodes.overview: The No. 1 Contender to challenge Seth Rollins for the NXT Championship is decided in a Fatal 4-Way Elimination Match between Justin Gabriel, Bo Dallas, Drew McIntyre, and Jinder Mahal. Bray Wyatt introduces the world to his newest follower, Luke Harper. Plus, Roman Reigns puts everyone on notice, Kassius Ohno battles Trent Barreta, and more.

episodes.name: NXT 143
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Jinder Mahal's opportunity at the NXT Championship is at stake when he battles Bo Dallas in the main event. Aksana's poor judgment leads her to a match against Layla. Plus, Roman Reigns competes in singles action, Yoshi Tatsu and Percy Watson take on The Ascension, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 144
episodes.overview: When Trent Barreta is found attacked and unable to compete in the main event, NXT Commissioner Dusty Rhodes gives Kassius Ohno an unexpected surprise. Jinder Mahal makes a statement at the expense of NXT Champion Seth Rollins. Plus, Paige in action, Big E looks to settle a score with Camacho, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 145
episodes.overview: Hellfire and brimstone engulfs this edition of NXT, as Team Hell No puts the WWE Tag Team Championship on the line in a main event battle against Johnny Curtis and Michael McGillicutty. Violence erupts when Jinder Mahal and NXT Champion Seth Rollins meet face-to-face. Plus, Xavier Woods in action, Leo Kruger takes on Trent Barreta, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 146
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Kassius Ohno makes his presence felt when Tyson Kidd takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Leo Kruger in the main event. Axl Keegan makes his NXT debut by taking on Bo Dallas in singles competition. United States Champion Cesaro returns to take on Michael McGillicutty. All this and much more action!

episodes.name: NXT 147
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Seth Rollins' reign as NXT Champion is on the line when he defends his title against Jinder Mahal in the main event. NXT Commissioner Dusty Rhodes looks to put Vickie Guerrero in her place for her recent attempts to undermine his authority. Plus, Bray Wyatt introduces another follower, Paige takes on Sasha Banks, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 148
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Bo Dallas is faced with a large challenge when he faces World Heavyweight Champion Big Show in a non-title main event. Corey Graves sends an emphatic message to NXT Champion Seth Rollins. Plus, Big E Langston competes in a Handicap Match, Kassius Ohno goes one-on-one with Percy Watson, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 149
episodes.overview: As 2012 comes to close, Tony Dawson takes the WWE Universe on a journey through time to witness highlights of all the action and excitement that took place in NXT over the past year. Relive Seth Rollins becoming the first NXT Champion, the debut of Bray Wyatt, and much more on this special edition of NXT!

episodes.name: NXT 150
episodes.overview: In an effort to weaken The Shield, NXT Commissioner Dusty Rhodes orders Seth Rollins to defend the NXT Championship against Corey Graves in the main event. Kassius Ohno partners with Leo Kruger to take on Tyson Kidd and Justin Gabriel in a Tag Team Match. Plus, Sasha Banks, Bo Dallas, and more in action!

episodes.name: NXT 151
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Seth Rollins' unprecedented reign as the first ever NXT Champion may come to an abrupt ending when Rollins defends his title against Big E Langston in a No Disqualification Match main event. Plus, Paige in action, Luke Harper and Erick Rowan take on Yoshi Tatsu and Percy Watson, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 152
episodes.overview: Gravity becomes nonexistent on this edition of NXT, as Adrian Neville makes his debut. Following his recent victory to become the new NXT Champion, Big E Langston begins his reign by battling Camacho in a non-title match. Damien Sandow and United States Champion Antonio Cesaro face Justin Gabriel and Tyson Kidd in the main event. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 153
episodes.overview: Shawn Michaels comes to NXT to kick off a tournament to crown the first ever NXT Tag Team Champions. While several Superstars team up for this golden opportunity, Big E Langston takes to the ring to show everyone why he is the current NXT Champion. Plus, Sasha Banks, Corey Graves, and more in action.

episodes.name: NXT 154
episodes.overview: As the tournament to crown the first ever NXT Tag Team Champions continues, Bo Dallas and Michael McGillicutty look to advance in the competition by facing Primo and Epico in the main event. Plus, Mason Ryan takes on Sakamoto in singles action, Sasha Banks receives a letter from a secret admirer, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 155
episodes.overview: The teams of Kassius Ohno and Leo Kruger, Adrian Neville and Oliver Grey, The Wyatt Family, and Bo Dallas and Michael McGillicutty set their sights on advancing to the finals of the tournament to crown the first ever NXT Tag Team Champions. Plus, Conor O'Brian in action, Summer Rae explains her recent attack on Paige, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 156
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, the tournament to crown the first ever NXT Tag Team Champions concludes when The Wyatt Family's Luke Harper and Erick Rowan take on Oliver Grey and Adrian Neville for the gold in the main event. Plus, tensions between Paige and Summer Rae explode, Alex Riley battles Corey Graves, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 157
episodes.overview: After battling Yoshi Tatsu, Bray Wyatt punishes Luke Harper & Erick Rowan for failing to capture the NXT Tag Team Championship. The recent problems between The Ascension's Conor O'Brian and NXT Champion Big E Langston come to a head when they meet in the main event. Plus, Sasha Banks in action, Leo Kruger targets Tyson Kidd, and more.

episodes.name: NXT 158
episodes.overview: When Corey Graves, Bo Dallas, and The Ascension's Conor O'Brian compete in a Triple Threat Match to determine the Number One Contender for the NXT Championship, three familiar faces return to serve up a measure of justice. Plus, Emma meets Aksana in singles action, Justin Gabriel goes one-on-one with Leo Kruger, and more!

episodes.name: NXT 159
episodes.overview: After disrupting the plans of NXT Commissioner Dusty Rhodes on the previous edition of NXT, The Shield is banned from the arena. Corey Graves, Bo Dallas, and The Ascension's Conor O'Brian compete in a Triple Threat Match for a shot at the NXT Championship. Plus, Adrian Neville defends the NXT Tag Team Titles by himself and more.

episodes.name: NXT 160
episodes.overview: When World Heavyweight Champion Alberto Del Rio pays the Superstars of NXT a special visit, United States Champion Antonio Cesaro tries to seize an opportunity. Bo Dallas looks to settle a score with Bray Wyatt for costing him his shot at becoming the Number One Contender for the NXT Championship. All this and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 161
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Adrian Neville takes to the ring to go one-on-one with The Wyatt Family's Luke Harper in the main event. William Regal gets more than he bargained for when he offers an apology to Kassius Ohno. Plus, Bayley faces Paige in singles action, Justin Gabriel takes on Leo Kruger, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 162
episodes.overview: While preparing to team with Sheamus and Big Show against The Shield at WrestleMania, Randy Orton journeys to NXT to go one-on-one with Damien Sandow in the main event. Kaitlyn puts her Divas Championship on the line in a match against Natalya. All this and much more on this edition of NXT!

episodes.name: NXT 163
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Big E Langston puts the NXT Championship on the line against The Ascension's Conor O'Brian in the main event. Bo Dallas partners with Adrian Neville to take on The Wyatt Family's Luke Harper and Erick Rowan in a Tag Team Match. All this and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 164
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, the recent problems between Kassius Ohno and William Regal lead both men to face off against each other in the main event. The Shield return to NXT to take on Axl Keegan, Scott Dawson, and Percy Watson in a Six-Man Tag Team Match. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 165
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, The Shield's Seth Rollins returns to go one-on-one with Corey Graves in a Lumberjack Match main event. Summer Rae looks to take her rivalry with Paige to another level. Plus, Bray Wyatt takes to the ring for singles competition, Leo Kruger takes on Justin Gabriel, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 166
episodes.overview: Commissioner Dusty Rhodes proudly presents NXT's first ever Clash of the Champions. From Brad Maddox challenging Big E Langston for the NXT Championship, to Wade Barrett defending the Intercontinental Championship against Bo Dallas in the main event, several titles are at stake on this very special edition of NXT.

episodes.name: NXT 167
episodes.overview: After recently refusing to join Bray Wyatt and his Wyatt Family, Chris Jericho returns to NXT to go one-on-one with The Eater of Worlds in a memorable main event confrontation. While their leader prepares to face Y2J in singles action, Luke Harper and Erick Rowan compete in a Triple Threat Tag Team Elimination Match. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 168
episodes.overview: Tag Team Championship Match as Bo Dallas and Adrian Neville defend their title against The Wyatt Family. Also, the Anti-Diva Paige takes on newcomer Bayley.

episodes.name: NXT 169
episodes.overview: NXT Championship match between reigning Champ Big E Langston and Damien Sandow. Also Natalya visits NXT to take on Summer Rae.

episodes.name: NXT 170
episodes.overview: Antonio Cesaro takes on Yoshi Tatsu and NXT newcomer Sami Zayn. Also, Bray Wyatt vs. Corey Graves in the main event.

episodes.name: NXT 171
episodes.overview: A huge special announcement from WWE's Executive Vice President Stephanie McMahon. Also, a Battle Royal to decide the #1 Contender for the NXT Championship.

episodes.name: NXT 172
episodes.overview: Round 1 of the Women's Championship Tournament. Also, The Wyatt Family defends the Tag Team titles against Corey Graves and Kassius Ohno.

episodes.name: NXT 173
episodes.overview: Bo Dallas takes on Big E Langston for the NXT Championship. Also, the first round of the Women's Championship Tournament continues as Alicia Fox takes on Bayley.

episodes.name: NXT 174
episodes.overview: The Wyatt Family takes on Adrian Neville, Corey Graves and Kassius Ohno in a huge main event. Also, the Women's Championship Tournament continues as Summer Rae takes on Sasha Banks.

episodes.name: NXT 175
episodes.overview: The Women's Championship Tournament continues. Also, NXT's new Champion, Bo Dallas takes on Mickey Keegan.

episodes.name: NXT 176
episodes.overview: Bo Dallas defends the NXT Title against Antonio Cesaro. Also, Alicia Fox takes on Paige in the Women's Championship Semi-Finals.

episodes.name: NXT 177
episodes.overview: The Women's Championship Semi-Finals continue when Emma takes on Summer Rae. Also, The Wyatt Family vs. Antonio Cesaro, Leo Kruger and Sami Zayn.

episodes.name: NXT 178
episodes.overview: Tag Team Championship Match between defending Champions, The Wyatt Family and challengers Adrian Neville and Corey Graves. Also, the debut of NXT Diva, Charlotte.

episodes.name: NXT 179
episodes.overview: NXT Women's Title Match to crown the first ever NXT Women's Champion. Also, Sheamus pays a visit to Full Sail to take on The Wyatt Family.

episodes.name: NXT 180
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Bo Dallas teams up with Sami Zayn to take on Antonio Cesaro and Leo Kruger. Also featuring Tag Team Champions Corey Graves and Adrian Neville.

episodes.name: NXT 181
episodes.overview: Divas Dance Battle between Summer Rae and Emma. Also, a huge Championship main event as Bo Dallas defends the title against Leo Kruger.

episodes.name: NXT 182
episodes.overview: Paul Heyman and Curtis Axel pay a visit to NXT in search of the next "Paul Heyman Guy". Also, Paige defends the NXT Women's Title against Summer Rae.

episodes.name: NXT 183
episodes.overview: Divas Championship Match between Bailey and defending champ AJ Lee. Also, CJ Parker debuts and NXT gets a visit from The Showoff, Dolph Ziggler.

episodes.name: NXT 184
episodes.overview: After the attack to his Tag Team Partner Corey Graves, Adrian Neville challenges any member of The Ascension to avenge his fallen NXT Tag Team Championship partner.

episodes.name: NXT 185
episodes.overview: Tag Team Champion Corey Graves vs. Rick Victor of The Ascension. Also, Sami Zayn takes on Jack Swagger in a huge main event match up.

episodes.name: NXT 186
episodes.overview: NXT Women's Champion Paige takes on Sasha Banks. Also, Leo Kruger gets in the ring with Xavier Woods.

episodes.name: NXT 187
episodes.overview: Sami Zayn vs. Curt Hawkins and a huge main event 8 Man Tag Team Match.

episodes.name: NXT 188
episodes.overview: Amidst The Authority's problems with the entire Rhodes family on the main roster, Triple H comes to NXT to make a huge announcement. Several duos compete in a Tag Team Turmoil Match for an opportunity to challenge Corey Graves and Adrian Neville for the NXT Tag Team Championship. All this and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 189
episodes.overview: Fandango visits NXT for a mixed Tag Team match with dance partner Summer Rae. Also, The Ascension challenges NXT Tag Team Champions Adrian Neville and Corey Graves for the Titles.

episodes.name: NXT 190
episodes.overview: Rob Van Dam visits NXT to take on "The Artist" Aiden English. Also, Mojo Rawley makes an energetic debut.

episodes.name: NXT 191
episodes.overview: The Ascension defends the Tag Team Titles for the first time against former Champions Corey Graves and Adrian Neville. Also, the NXT Championship is on the line as Bo Dallas takes on Sami Zayn.

episodes.name: NXT 192
episodes.overview: Things heat up between Corey Graves and former Tag Team partner Adrian Neville. Also, Divas action as Emma takes on Sasha Banks.

episodes.name: NXT 193
episodes.overview: A huge Divas match up as NXT Women's Champion Paige takes on Summer Rae. Also, Tyler Breeze vs. CJ Parker in the main event.

episodes.name: NXT 194
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, the managerial relationship between Sylvester Lefort and Alexander Rusev comes to a screeching halt thanks to the arrival of a Russian femme fatale. Two brawlers clash in the main event when Luke Harper goes one-on-one with Kassius Ohno. Plus, Leo Kruger, Mojo Rawley, and many more in action!

episodes.name: NXT 195
episodes.overview: The intense and personal rivalry between Adrian Neville and Corey Graves explodes in a memorable 2-Out-of-3 Falls Match main event. Bayley partners with Charlotte to take on the duo of Summer Rae and Sasha Banks in a Tag Team Match. Plus, Mason Ryan, Camacho, and many more in action on this edition of NXT!

episodes.name: NXT 196
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Bo Dallas enjoys a special Homecoming Celebration. NXT General Manager John "Bradshaw" Layfield hesitantly reinstates Sami Zayn and announces a series of Beat the Clock Challenge Matches to determine a new No. 1 Contender for Dallas' title. Plus, Hunico & Camacho team up for action, Bayley addresses Charlotte's betrayal, and more.

episodes.name: NXT 197
episodes.overview: With an opportunity to compete for the NXT Championship on the line, Sami Zayn and Adrian Neville face off against each other in an incredible main event contest. While waiting to see who will challenge him for the NXT Title, Bo Dallas takes to the ring to go one-on-one with CJ Parker. All this and much more on this edition of NXT!

episodes.name: NXT 198
episodes.overview: Adrian Neville gears up and takes to the ring to challenge Bo Dallas for the NXT Championship in the main event. Two wrestling dynasties clash when Paige defends the NXT Women's Championship in a match against Natalya. Antonio Cesaro's search for William Regal leads him to make an example out of Byron Saxton. All this and more!

episodes.name: NXT 199
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Leo Kruger looks to settle a score with Sami Zayn in the main event. The Ascension's Conor O'Brian and Rick Victor put the NXT Tag Team Championship on the line in a match against Hunico and Camacho. Plus, Sasha Banks in action, Alexander Rusev goes one-on-one with Kassius Ohno, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 200
episodes.overview: On the special 200th episode of NXT, Adrian Neville receives another opportunity at the NXT Championship when he challenges Bo Dallas for the gold in a Lumberjack Match main event. The Ascension defends the NXT Tag Team Titles against The American Pitbulls. Plus, Sami Zayn in action, Sasha Banks takes on NXT Women's Champion Paige, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 201
episodes.overview: As 2013 comes to a close, Renee Young takes the WWE Universe on an NXT Rewind to recap all the action and excitement that took place over the past year. Plus, an exclusive look at the brand new WWE Performance Center, Antonio Cesaro goes one-on-one with William Regal, and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 202
episodes.overview: On this edition of NXT, Sami Zayn and Leo Kruger look to settle their ongoing rivalry in a 2-Out-of-3 Falls Match main event. Natalya goes one-on-one with Emma in a match to determine the Number One Contender for the NXT Women's Championship. Alexander Rusev takes to the ring to battle Kofi Kingston. All this and much more!

episodes.name: NXT 203
episodes.overview: On the orders of The Authority, WWE Director of Operations Kane comes to NXT to punish Xavier Woods by forcing him to go one-on-one with Alexander Rusev. NXT Tag Team Champions The Ascension take on Hunico and Camacho in a Tornado Tag Team Match main event. Plus, Tyson Kidd, Colin Cassady, and many more in action!

episodes.name: NXT 204
episodes.overview: Triple H returns to Full Sail University to make a huge announcement regarding the future of NXT. Kofi Kingston takes to the ring to go one-on-one with Alexander Rusev in a competitive main event confrontation. Plus, Adrian Neville looks to settle a score with Tyler Breeze in singles action, NXT Champion Bo Dallas faces CJ Parker, and more.

episodes.name: NXT 205
episodes.overview: With the future of NXT destined for the WWE Network, Bo Dallas' reign as NXT Champion may be running short of time after Triple H orders Dallas to battle Adrian Neville in a Beat the Clock Match main event. Plus, Antonio Cesaro returns to meet CJ Parker in a singles confrontation, Natalya goes one-on-one with Summer Rae, and much more!

episodes.name: January 6, 2016
episodes.overview: Relive more of WWE NXT's best moments from 2015 with these video highlights. Videos courtesy of the award-winning WWE Network.

episodes.name: January 13, 2016
episodes.overview: NXT General Manager William Regal wasted no time in kicking 2016 off the right way. After thanking the NXT Universe for their incredible support in 2015 and reiterating that Bayley’s next challenger would be determined in the evening’s main event, Regal welcomed Sami Zayn back to the Full Sail Arena for the first time since his injury.

episodes.name: January 20, 2016
episodes.overview: Tensions are high in NXT, to say the least. With their NXT Championship No. 1 Contender’s Triple Threat Match just one week away, Sami Zayn, Samoa Joe and Baron Corbin were all in action, tuning up for their biggest match of 2016 so far. Plus, NXT Women’s Champion Bayley joined forces with the No. 1 Contender to her title, her best friend Carmella, to take on two women furious that The Princess of Staten Island won last week’s Battle Royal, Alexa Bliss and Emma.

episodes.name: January 27, 2016
episodes.overview: With Sami Zayn, Samoa Joe and Baron Corbin all staking claims to the next NXT Championship Match, the NXT Universe was excited to finally answer the question of who the next No. 1 contender would be after tonight’s main event. However, the controversial conclusion of the Triple Threat Match only caused more questions to be asked as Finn Bálor waits in the wings, ready to defend his title.

episodes.name: February 3, 2016
episodes.overview: After the controversial ending to last week’s NXT Championship No. 1 Contender’s Triple Threat Match, NXT General Manager William Regal made a ruling that sent shockwaves through NXT. Sami Zayn and Samoa Joe will square off, with a future championship showdown with Finn Bálor hanging in the balance, a decision that left Baron Corbin furious. Meanwhile, the NXT Champion found himself facing another tough test in non-title action against Apollo Crews, who was looking to prove himself as worthy.

episodes.name: February 10, 2016
episodes.overview: NXT made its debut at the CFE Arena on the campus of the University of Central Florida with a huge main event featuring best friends Carmella and NXT Women’s Champion Bayley clashing for the title. The impending battle left the NXT Universe wondering two things: Who would leave as champion, and would their friendship survive?

episodes.name: February 17, 2016
episodes.overview: Heading into this week’s show, the NXT Universe was looking for the answer to one question – Who is the No. 1 Contender to the NXT Championship? However, after a hard-fought battle between Sami Zayn and Samoa Joe, there were more questions left to be asked as controversy left Finn Bálor without a top challenger once again.

episodes.name: February 24, 2016
episodes.overview: Payback was on the minds of NXT Women’s Champion Bayley & Carmella as they got ready for this week’s main event. The best friends were itching to get their hands on Eva Marie & Nia Jax, who put a damper on their hard-fought title match two weeks ago. Would their desire for retribution be enough to bring them victory?

episodes.name: March 2, 2016
episodes.overview: NXT’s run at the University of Central Florida’s CFE Arena came to a close this week with an absolutely massive show. NXT General Manager William Regal made a major announcement —the signing of Austin Aries! Plus, two of the longest-reigning NXT Champions in history clashed in the main event, as current titleholder Finn Bálor locked up with The Man That Gravity Forgot, Neville!

episodes.name: March 9, 2016
episodes.overview: NXT General Manager William Regal had an action-packed Wednesday night planned for the NXT Universe. Fans were treated to exactly that, but not quite in the way Regal had planned. What was scheduled to be a show featuring American Alpha, The Vaudevillains, NXT Women’s Champion Bayley, Asuka and more was instead taken over by a single match – the 2-out-of-3 Falls war between Sami Zayn and Samoa Joe to determine the No.1  Contender to Finn Bálor’s NXT Championship.

episodes.name: March 16, 2016
episodes.overview: With NXT TakeOver: Dallas just over two weeks away, NXT General Manager William Regal began revealing more of the card taking place on Friday, April 1, two days before WrestleMania 32. NXT Women’s Champion Bayley found out who she will be defending her title against, while Sami Zayn got a huge surprise from Regal. Plus, in the main event, two of NXT’s top teams clashed with an NXT Tag Team Championship opportunity hanging in the balance.

episodes.name: March 23, 2016
episodes.overview: With just nine days left before TakeOver: Dallas, the stakes have never been higher in NXT. Finn Bálor set out to prove that he’s ready to weather Samoa Joe’s worst in the Lone Star State, while the submission specialist sent a message to the NXT Champion in brutal fashion. Meanwhile, Asuka looked to continue along the path of destruction that led her to a showdown with NXT Women’s Champion Bayley in Dallas, taking on Emma in the main event.

episodes.name: March 30, 2016
episodes.overview: The road to TakeOver: Dallas made its final stop at Full Sail University, just two days before the hottest brand in sports-entertainment invades the Lone Star State. Many of the competitors set for action during Friday’s extravaganza took to the ring Wednesday night to make final adjustments before the biggest night of their careers. Who came out looking strong heading into the historic WWE Network broadcast?

episodes.name: April 6, 2016
episodes.overview:
Just days removed from the epic TakeOver: Dallas special, this week’s edition of NXT took a special look back at the incredible night, including American Alpha’s and Asuka’s big championship victories, Shinsuke Nakamura’s unforgettable debut and the all-out war between NXT Champion Finn Bálor and Samoa Joe.

Plus, in the main event, “The Drifter” Elias Samson sought to silence Apollo Crews once and for all, while Crews looked to capitalize on the momentum from his huge Raw debut and send Samson drifting away.

episodes.name: April 13, 2016
episodes.overview: With NXT TakeOver: Dallas in the rear-view mirror, the Superstars of NXT are jockeying for position as the champions look for their next contenders. Meanwhile, the NXT Universe were on the edge of their seats waiting for this week’s main event, featuring the Wednesday night debut of The King of Strong Style, Shinsuke Nakamura.

episodes.name: April 20, 2016
episodes.overview: As some of NXT’s most popular stars make an impact on Raw and SmackDown, there’s never been a better time for the rest of the roster to try to make their mark between the yellow ropes, or for some new faces to introduce themselves to the NXT Universe. This week featured some of both, as new NXT Tag Team Champions American Alpha accepted the challenge of Enzo Amore & Colin Cassady, and Apollo Crews found himself in the crosshairs of Samoa Joe. Plus, the fun-loving No Way Jose made his NXT debut!

episodes.name: April 27, 2016
episodes.overview: The NXT Universe was still reeling from last Thursday’s shocking news that Samoa Joe had captured the NXT Championship from Finn Bálor. The Demon’s record-breaking 292-day reign as champion has ended, and a furious submission specialist now stands atop NXT. What will Samoa Joe’s huge victory mean for the future of NXT?

episodes.name: May 4, 2016
episodes.overview: Much has changed since NXT’s last event in Orlando. All three championships have changed hands, with Samoa Joe standing atop the mountain as NXT Champion. The rest of the roster is scrambling for the right to challenge for the titles, but as NXT becomes the place to be in sports-entertainment, the NXT Superstars are finding themselves competing with new challengers from outside the ranks of WWE.

episodes.name: May 11, 2016
episodes.overview: Finn Bálor made his long-awaited return to NXT this week, his first appearance since Samoa Joe ended his 292-day reign as NXT Champion. The Demon didn’t mince words, saying that all of his matches with the submission specialist could have gone either way. But before he could elaborate, his opponent in the main event, Elias Samson, interrupted Bálor with a song mocking the former champion. Bálor put an end to the impromptu concert, silencing The Drifter with a Pele Kick ahead of their battle.

episodes.name: May 18, 2016
episodes.overview: As the NXT Universe was still reeling from the major announcement that Samoa Joe and Finn Bálor’s huge NXT Championship Match at TakeOver would be contested inside a steel cage, they were surprised for a second time this week, as two of NXT’s newest stars joined forces for a big tag team encounter!

episodes.name: May 25, 2016
episodes.overview: After the brutal ending to last week’s match between Bayley and Nia Jax, NXT General Manager William Regal revealed that Bayley was not cleared to compete and would not be cleared in time to get her rematch against NXT Women’s Champion Asuka at TakeOver on June 8. Though Bayley will get her opportunity down the line, Regal announced that Nia Jax, Carmella and Alexa Bliss would square off in the evening’s main event to determine Asuka’s challenger in two weeks.

episodes.name: June 1, 2016
episodes.overview: Tensions were running high in NXT, with TakeOver: The End… just one week away. Everyone was on edge, including NXT Tag Team Champions The Revival. Scott Dawson & Dash Wilder declared that they were going to take back their titles from American Alpha. Johnny Gargano & Tommaso Ciampa disagreed, saying that not only can’t The Revival beat Jason Jordan & Chad Gable, Dash & Dawson couldn’t beat them. The trash-talking led to a scuffle between the two teams, with Gargano & Ciampa sending the No. 1 contenders scrambling up the ramp, setting the stage for a showdown between the duos later in the evening.

episodes.name: June 15, 2016
episodes.overview: Finn Bálor took to the ring to ask what was next for him after coming up short at TakeOver. It didn't take long for Bálor to find out what lies ahead, as Shinsuke Nakamura issued a challenge to the former NXT Champion!

episodes.name: June 22, 2016
episodes.overview: The huge challenge laid out to Finn Bálor by Shinsuke Nakamura was all the NXT Universe could talk about since last Wednesday.
