episodes.overview: Finn Bálor teams with Undisputed ERA's Kyle O’Reilly to take on Oney Lorcan & Danny Burch. In the Dusty Rhodes Tag Team Classic, Kushida & Leon Ruff face The Grizzled Young Veterans, and MSK battle Killian Dain & Drake Maverick. Raquel González & Dakota Kai clash with Aliyah & Jessi Kamea in the Women’s Dusty Rhodes Tag Team Classic.

episodes.name: February 3, 2021
episodes.overview: Royal Rumble Match winner Edge comes to NXT. Tommaso Ciampa & Timothy Thatcher battle The Undisputed ERA, and Lucha House Party face Legado del Fantasma in the Dusty Cup Quarterfinals. Kayden Carter & Kacy Catanzaro clash with Dakota Kai & Raquel Gonzalez in the Women's Dusty Cup Semifinals.

episodes.name: February 10, 2021
episodes.overview: The Dusty Rhodes Tag Team Classic continues. Ember Moon & Shotzi Blackheart take on Candice LeRae & Indi Hartwell in the Women’s Dusty Cup. On the men's side, Tommaso Ciampa & Timothy Thatcher battle The Grizzled Young Veterans, and MSK face Legado del Fantasma. NXT Champion Finn Bálor comes face-to-face with Pete Dunne.

episodes.name: February 14, 2021 - NXT Takeover: Vengeance Day
episodes.overview: Love is in the air — and vengeance isn't far behind. Finn Bálor defends the NXT Championship against Pete Dunne. Tag teams battle in the Men’s and Women’s Dusty Cup Finals. Io Shirai, Toni Storm and Mercedes Martinez square off in an NXT Women's Championship Triple Threat Match.

episodes.name: February 17, 2021
episodes.overview: Kyle O'Reilly looks for answers after Adam Cole's betrayal at NXT TakeOver: Vengeance Day. MSK and Raquel González & Dakota Kai celebrate their Men's and Women's Dusty Rhodes Tag Team Classic victories. Shotzi Blackheart & Ember Moon battle The Way’s Candice LeRae & Indi Hartwell.

episodes.name: February 24, 2021
episodes.overview: Adam Cole vows to explain his actions after his shocking betrayal at NXT TakeOver: Vengeance Day. Karrion Kross collides with Santos Escobar in a No Disqualification Match. Following her impressive NXT debut, Zoey Stark goes head-to-head with NXT Women's Champion Io Shirai in a non-title match. Johnny Gargano faces Dexter Lumis.

episodes.name: March 3, 2021
episodes.overview: WWE Women's Tag Team Champions Nia Jax & Shayna Baszler come to NXT to defend their titles against Raquel González & Dakota Kai. The Way head to therapy to sort out their feelings over Dexter Lumis. LA Knight addresses the NXT Universe. NXT Tag Team Champions Danny Burch & Oney Lorcan face Tommaso Ciampa & Timothy Thatcher in a non-title bout.

episodes.name: March 10, 2021
episodes.overview: Finn Bálor defends the NXT Championship against Adam Cole. Io Shirai clashes with Toni Storm for the NXT Women's Championship. NXT General Manager William Regal makes two major announcements that change the landscape of the black-and-gold brand.

episodes.name: March 17, 2021
episodes.overview: Karrion Kross sets his sights on NXT Champion Finn Bálor. LA Knight makes his NXT in-ring debut. Jordan Devlin heads to NXT to prove he’s the “real” NXT Cruiserweight Champion. Dexter Lumis battles Austin Theory.

episodes.name: March 24, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT General Manager William Regal promises to settle Adam Cole and Kyle O'Reilly's conflict after they were apprehended by police. NXT Women's Tag Team Champions Shotzi Blackheart & Ember Moon battle Aliyah & Mercedes Martinez. Drake Maverick goes up against NXT UK Champion WALTER in a non-title match. Oney Lorcan collides with Karrion Kross.

episodes.name: March 31, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT Superstars look to make a statement on the final episode of NXT before the first-ever two-night NXT TakeOver. Twelve men collide in a Battle Royal to see who will qualify for the Gauntlet Eliminator Match on Night 1 of NXT TakeOver: Stand & Deliver. Raquel González battles Zoey Stark before she challenges for the NXT Women's Title.

episodes.name: April 7, 2021 - NXT TakeOver: Stand & Deliver - Night 1
episodes.overview: It’s the biggest NXT TakeOver in history. On Night 1 of the first-ever, two-night NXT TakeOver, NXT Women's Champion Io Shirai defends her title against Raquel González, and Tommaso Ciampa challenges WALTER for the NXT United Kingdom Championship.

episodes.name: April 8, 2021 - NXT TakeOver: Stand & Deliver - Night 2
episodes.overview: It’s the biggest NXT TakeOver in history. On Night 2 of the first-ever, two-night NXT TakeOver, Finn Bálor defends his NXT Championship against Karrion Kross, and former Undisputed ERA brothers Adam Cole and Kyle O'Reilly settle their saga in an Unsanctioned Match.

episodes.name: April 13, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Karrion Kross and NXT Women's Champion Raquel Gonzalez begin their title reigns amid the fallout from NXT TakeOver: Stand & Deliver. Franky Monet arrives on NXT. NXT Cruiserweight Champion Santos Escobar issues an open challenge. MSK defend their NXT Tag Team Titles against Killian Dain & Drake Maverick.

episodes.name: April 20, 2021
episodes.overview: Kyle O'Reilly returns after prevailing in a savage Unsanctioned Match against Adam Cole at NXT TakeOver: Stand & Deliver. Sarray makes her debut against Zoey Stark. Kushida issues an open challenge for his NXT Cruiserweight Title. Dexter Lumis collides with LA Knight.

episodes.name: April 27, 2021
episodes.overview: Adam Cole speaks for the first time following his Unsanctioned Match at NXT TakeOver: Stand & Deliver in an exclusive sit-down interview. Kushida joins forces with MSK to battle Legado del Fantasma. Bronson Reed faces Austin Theory for an NXT North American Title opportunity. Mercedes Martinez takes on Dakota Kai.

episodes.name: May 4, 2021
episodes.overview: Finn Bálor returns for the first time since his defeat at NXT TakeOver: Stand & Deliver. Shotzi Blackheart & Ember Moon defend the NXT Women’s Tag Team Titles in a Street Fight against The Way. Leon Ruff and Isaiah “Swerve” Scott battle in a Falls Count Anywhere Match. Tommaso Ciampa & Timothy Thatcher square off with The Grizzled Young Veterans.

episodes.name: May 11, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT Women's Champion Raquel Gonzalez defends her title against Mercedes Martinez. NXT Cruiserweight Champion Kushida faces Santos Escobar in a 2-out-of-3 Falls Match. NXT Champion Karrion Kross clashes with Austin Theory in a non-title bout.

episodes.name: May 18, 2021
episodes.overview: Bronson Reed challenges Johnny Gargano for the NXT North American Championship inside a steel cage. “The Million Dollar Man" Ted DiBiase brings his legendary wealth to NXT. Zoey Stark battles Toni Storm in a rematch. Pete Dunne sits down for an exclusive interview with Arash Markazi.

episodes.name: May 25, 2021
episodes.overview: It's Karrion Kross vs. Finn Bálor II as The Prince looks to recapture the NXT Championship. Cameron Grimes encounters WWE Hall of Famer Ted DiBiase in a Million Dollar Faceoff. Franky Monet makes her highly-anticipated NXT in-ring debut. New NXT North American Champion Bronson Reed addresses the NXT Universe.

episodes.name: June 1, 2021
episodes.overview: Kyle O'Reilly, Pete Dunne and Johnny Gargano collide in a Triple Threat Match with the winner getting an NXT Title Match against Karrion Kross at NXT TakeOver: In Your House. NXT Tag Team Champions MSK defend their titles against Legado del Fantasma.

episodes.name: NXT #617
episodes.overview: Karrion Kross confronts the four men who will challenge for his NXT Championship at NXT TakeOver: In Your House. Ted DiBiase makes a “Priceless” announcement. Before Ember Moon gets her hands on Raquel Gonzalez, the former NXT Women’s Champion battles Dakota Kai.

episodes.name: June 13, 2021 - NXT Takeover: In Your House
episodes.overview: Karrion Kross defends the NXT Championship in a Fatal 5-Way Match against Adam Cole, Johnny Gargano, Kyle O'Reilly and Pete Dunne. Ember Moon challenges Raquel Gonzalez for the NXT Women's Title.

episodes.name: June 15, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT General Manager William Regal makes a big announcement. Tommaso Ciampa & Timothy Thatcher battle The Grizzled Young Veterans in a Tornado Tag Team Match. “The Million Dollar Man” Ted DiBiase presents LA Knight with his title in a Million Dollar Championship Coronation. Former NXT Women's Champion Io Shirai addresses the NXT Universe.

episodes.name: June 22, 2021
episodes.overview: Kyle O'Reilly tests himself against NXT Cruiserweight Champion Kushida in a non-title match. Adam Cole is in action. The mysterious Diamond Mine arrive at NXT. Franky Monet delivers her World Premiere Encore. Io Shirai & Zoey Stark battle The Robert Stone Brand. Ever-Rise seek retribution against Hit Row.

episodes.name: June 29, 2021
episodes.overview: Isaiah "Swerve" Scott challenges Bronson Reed for the NXT North American Title. Kyle O'Reilly and Adam Cole's rivalry escalates ahead of NXT Great American Bash. Io Shirai & Zoey Stark, Raquel Gonzalez & Dakota Kai and Shotzi Blackheart & Ember Moon battle in a NXT Women's Tag Team Titles No. 1 Contender’s Triple Threat Tag Match.

episodes.name: July 6, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT Great American Bash returns as Kyle O'Reilly and Adam Cole look to settle their heated rivalry once and for all. LA Knight defends the Million Dollar Title against Cameron Grimes. NXT Champion Karrion Kross and Johnny Gargano meet face-to-face. Timothy Thatcher & Tommaso Ciampa challenge MSK for the NXT Tag Team Titles.

episodes.name: July 13, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Karrion Kross defends his title against Johnny Gargano with Samoa Joe as special guest referee. Ikemen Jiro and Duke Hudson kick off the NXT Breakout Tournament. Cameron Grimes’ duties as LA Knight's butler begin. Ember Moon faces Dakota Kai. Dexter Lumis clashes with Santos Escobar. Sarray accepts a challenge from Gigi Dolin.

episodes.name: July 20, 2021
episodes.overview: Raquel Gonzalez defends the NXT Women's Championship against Xia Li. Samoa Joe searches for payback against NXT Champion Karrion Kross. Odyssey Jones faces Andre Chase in the NXT Breakout Tournament. Legado del Fantasma host their very own "Mariachi Musical Madness." Kyle O'Reilly battles Austin Theory. LA Knight clashes with Drake Maverick.

episodes.name: July 27, 2021
episodes.overview: Bronson Reed looks to seize a golden opportunity against Adam Cole. NXT Women's Champion Raquel Gonzalez faces a betrayal. Samoa Joe offers William Regal a solution to his Karrion Kross problem. The NXT Breakout Tournament continues. Imperium battle Hit Row.

episodes.name: August 3, 2021
episodes.overview: Johnny Gargano and Dexter Lumis battle over Indi Hartwell in a Love Her or Lose Her Match. NXT Champion Karrion Kross and Samoa Joe's conflict heats up ahead of their NXT TakeOver 36 clash. LA Knight and his butler Cameron Grimes team up to take on The Grizzled Young Veterans. Hit Row face Legado del Fantasma in a tag team showdown.

episodes.name: August 10, 2021
episodes.overview: Kyle O'Reilly and Adam Cole's explosive face-to-face meeting sets the stage for their Undisputed Finale. In his first NXT appearance, Ilja Dragunov collides with Pete Dunne. "The Million Dollar Man" Ted DiBiase places a risky bet on Cameron Grimes. The NXT Breakout Tournament moves into the semifinals.

episodes.name: August 17, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Karrion Kross and Samoa Joe meet face-to-face ahead of their title clash at NXT TakeOver 36. MSK and Imperium battle for the NXT Tag Team Titles. Dexter Lumis & Indi Hartwell's Mixed Tag Team Match against Robert Stone & Jessi Kamea sparks a stunning turn of events.

episodes.name: August 22, 2021 - NXT Takeover 36
episodes.overview: Samoa Joe returns to the ring to challenge Karrion Kross for the NXT Championship. WALTER looks to continue his legendary NXT UK Title reign in a jaw-dropping rematch against Ilja Dragunov.

episodes.name: August 24, 2021
episodes.overview: The 2021 NXT Breakout Tournament concludes with a final showdown between Odyssey Jones and Carmelo Hayes. Legado del Fantasma face Hit Row. Ridge Holland battles Timothy Thatcher. Kay Lee Ray makes her NXT in-ring debut against Valentina Feroz.

episodes.name: August 31, 2021
episodes.overview: Tommaso Ciampa looks to get even with Ridge Holland. New NXT UK Champion Ilja Dragunov addresses NXT following his triumph at NXT TakeOver 36. Johnny Gargano collides with LA Knight. Kyle O’Reilly seeks retribution against Duke Hudson. Ikemen Jiro accepts Roderick Strong’s open challenge.

episodes.name: September 7, 2021
episodes.overview: MSK defend their NXT Tag Team Championship against Oney Lorcan & Danny Burch. Io Shirai & Zoey Stark battle Kacy Catanzaro & Kayden Carter for the NXT Women’s Tag Team Championship. Julius & Brutus Creed of The Diamond Mine make their debut. Mei Ying competes inside the squared circle for the first time.

episodes.name: September 14, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT 2.0 is here! It's a brand-new era in the rich history of NXT as a Fatal 4-Way Match determines the new NXT Champion. Indi Hartwell and Dexter Lumis head to the altar for their highly-anticipated InDex wedding. New faces arrive to make their mark.

episodes.name: September 21, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Tommaso Ciampa kicks off his reign in chaotic fashion. Kushida collides with Roderick Strong in an NXT Cruiserweight Championship Match. Toxic Attraction address the NXT Universe. An influx of new faces establish themselves in NXT 2.0.

episodes.name: September 28, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT Women's Champion Raquel Gonzalez defends her title against Franky Monet. Io Shirai & Zoey Stark battle Toxic Attraction for the NXT Women’s Tag Team Titles. Indi Hartwell and Dexter Lumis turn up the heat on their honeymoon. Lash Legend debuts her new talk show, “Lashing Out with Lash Legend.” Kyle O'Reilly collides with Ridge Holland.

episodes.name: October 5, 2021
episodes.overview: MSK, Brooks Jensen & Josh Briggs, Grizzled Young Veterans and Carmelo Hayes & Trick Williams clash in an NXT Tag Team Title Fatal 4-Way Elimination Match. A new challenger confronts NXT Champion Tommaso Ciampa. Mandy Rose faces Ember Moon.

episodes.name: October 12, 2021
episodes.overview: Without his Hit Row teammates by his side, Isaiah "Swerve" Scott defends his NXT North American Title against Santos Escobar. Joe Gacy battles Tommaso Ciampa in a high-stakes showdown. Kyle O’Reilly teams with Von Wagner against Pete Dunne & Ridge Holland.

episodes.name: October 19, 2021
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Tommaso Ciampa joins forces with his rival Bron Breakker to take on The Grizzled Young Veterans. An opportunity to Spin the Wheel, Make the Deal for the upcoming NXT Women’s Tag Team Title Match is on the line. Grayson Waller faces LA Knight for the right to host Halloween Havoc.

episodes.name: October 26, 2021 - NXT Halloween Havoc
episodes.overview: Tommaso Ciampa defends the NXT Championship against Bron Breakker. Halloween Havoc comes to NXT 2.0 with Spin the Wheel, Make the Deal, the Scareway to Hell Ladder Match, Dexter Lumis and Johnny Gargano's haunted house and Chucky.

episodes.name: November 2, 2021
episodes.overview: Carmelo Hayes & Trick Williams take on Johnny Gargano & Dexter Lumis. NXT Women's Champion Mandy Rose begins her title reign. Cameron Grimes steps into Duke Hudson's Poker Room. Tony D’Angelo joins “Lashing Out with Lash Legend." Von Wagner & Kyle O'Reilly battle Legado del Fantasma.

episodes.name: November 9, 2021
episodes.overview: Io Shirai, Kacy Catanzaro & Kayden Carter battle Toxic Attraction. Pete Dunne makes a statement. Kay Lee Ray faces Sarray. The Creed Brothers collide with Jacket Time. Boa goes head-to-head with Joe Gacy.

episodes.name: November 16, 2021
episodes.overview: Raquel Gonzalez and Dakota Kai reignite their rivalry in a head-to-head showdown. Tony D'Angelo collides with Dexter Lumis. Odyssey Jones joins forces with Jacket Time to take on Diamond Mine. Cameron Grimes and Duke Hudson sit down for one final hand of Texas Hold ’Em.

episodes.name: November 23, 2021
episodes.overview: Carmelo Hayes defends the NXT North American Title in a Triple Threat Match against Johnny Gargano and Pete Dunne. Kacy Catanzaro & Kayden Carter battle Indi Hartwell & Persia Pirotta. Mandy Rose faces Cora Jade as the battlelines are drawn ahead of NXT WarGames.

episodes.name: November 30, 2021
episodes.overview: Kay Lee Ray and Dakota Kai go to battle in a WarGames Advantage Ladder Match. The NXT Universe decides who will compete for the new school and old school teams in a WarGames Advantage Ladder Match. Joe Gacy hosts an "All-Inclusive Invitational."

episodes.name: December 5, 2021 - NXT WarGames
episodes.overview: It's old school vs. new school as two generations of NXT Superstars collide in a WarGames Match. NXT Champion Tommaso Ciampa leads his fellow NXT originals into battle against NXT North American Champion Carmelo Hayes and the up-and-coming combatants of NXT 2.0.

episodes.name: December 7, 2021
episodes.overview: Johnny Gargano addresses the NXT Universe after an emotional battle at NXT WarGames. Former tag team partners Kyle O'Reilly and Von Wagner clash inside a steel cage. NXT North American Champion Carmelo Hayes collides with Dexter Lumis. Santos Escobar battles Xyon Quinn.

episodes.name: December 14, 2021
episodes.overview: Bron Breakker collides with Roderick Strong. Cameron Grimes and Duke Hudson battle in a No Holds Barred Match. Grayson Waller responds to his attack on Johnny Gargano. Harland makes his in-ring debut. Cora Jade faces Dakota Kai.

episodes.name: December 21, 2021
episodes.overview: AJ Styles comes to NXT 2.0 to confront Grayson Waller. Raquel Gonzalez battles Dakota Kai in a Street Fight. Pete Dunne collides with Tony D'Angelo. The Creed Brothers take on GYV. Dexter Lumis faces Trick Williams.

episodes.name: December 28, 2021
episodes.overview: The NXT Women's Championship takes center stage ahead of New Year's Evil. Grayson Waller addresses his confrontation with AJ Styles on Raw. Matt Riddle and MSK call out Imperium. Carmelo Hayes and Roderick Strong sign their New Year’s Evil Championship Unification Match contract.

episodes.name: January 4, 2022
episodes.overview: It's New Year's Evil as Tommaso Ciampa defends the NXT Title against Bron Breakker. Mandy Rose, Raquel Gonzalez and Cora Jade battle for the NXT Women's Title. Carmelo Hayes faces Roderick Strong in a Championship Unification Match. WALTER returns to lead Imperium against Riddle & MSK. AJ Styles comes calling for Grayson Waller.

episodes.name: January 11, 2022
episodes.overview: AJ Styles faces Grayson Waller in a highly-anticipated showdown. Bron Breakker kicks off his NXT Championship reign. Pete Dunne battles Tony D'Angelo in a Crowbar on a Pole Match. Indi Hartwell, Persia Pirotta & Wendy Choo take on Kacy Catanzaro, Kayden Carter & Amari Miller.

episodes.name: January 18, 2022
episodes.overview: WALTER arrives at NXT 2.0 in a main event showdown against Roderick Strong. Tony D'Angelo hosts a "memorial service" for Pete Dunne. The 2022 Men's Dusty Rhodes Classic Tournament begins. Kay Lee Ray collides with Ivy Nile.

episodes.name: January 25, 2022
episodes.overview: Cameron Grimes and Tony D'Angelo battle for an NXT North American Title opportunity. Kay Lee Ray joins forces with Indi Hartwell & Persia Pirotta to take on Toxic Attraction. Solo Sikoa and Boa collide in No Disqualification, Falls Count Anywhere Match. The first round of the Dusty Classic continues. OllieJayy performs live.

episodes.name: NXT #659
episodes.overview: Factions collide as Diamond Mine battle Imperium in a Six-Man Tag Team Match. NXT Champion Bron Breakker & Tommaso Ciampa join forces to take on Legado del Fantasma. Cora Jade clashes with Raquel Gonzalez. Joe Gacy attempts to help LA Knight "move on" in singles action.

episodes.name: NXT #660
episodes.overview: Kay Lee Ray challenges Mandy Rose for the NXT Women's Championship. NXT Champion Bron Breakker and Santos Escobar hold a Championship Summit. MSK face Malik Blade & Edris Enofé, and The Creed Brothers battle GYV in the Dusty Classic Semifinals.

episodes.name: NXT #661 - Vengeance Day
episodes.overview: NXT Vengeance Day is here as Bron Breakker clashes with Santos Escobar for the NXT Title. MSK face The Creed Brothers in the Dusty Classic Final. NXT Women's Tag Team Champions Toxic Attraction battle Indi Hartwell & Persia Pirotta. Pete Dunne collides with Tony D'Angelo in a Weaponized Steel Cage Match.

episodes.name: NXT #662
episodes.overview: Tommaso Ciampa battles Dolph Ziggler. The 2022 Women’s Dusty Classic begins. LA Knight looks for payback on Grayson Waller.

episodes.name: NXT #663
episodes.overview: Carmelo Hayes and Pete Dunne collide in an NXT North American Championship Match. NXT Champion Bron Breakker joins forces with Tommaso Ciampa in a tag team showdown against The Dirty Dawgs. Solo Sikoa clashes with Gunther.

episodes.name: NXT #664
episodes.overview: NXT Roadblock arrives as Bron Breakker, Tommaso Ciampa and Dolph Ziggler collide in a Triple Threat Match for the NXT Championship. LA Knight battles Grayson Waller in a Last Man Standing Match. The Creed Brothers challenge Imperium for the NXT Tag Team Championship. The Women's Dusty Classic continues.

episodes.name: NXT #665
episodes.overview: The Miz hosts a special NXT 2.0 edition of "Miz TV" with new NXT Champion Dolph Ziggler. Cameron Grimes faces Santos Escobar in a Qualifying Match for Carmelo Hayes' North American Championship Ladder Match. A-Kid makes his NXT 2.0 debut.

episodes.name: NXT #666
episodes.overview: Io Shirai & Kay Lee Ray face Wendy Choo & Dakota Kai in the Women's Dusty Rhodes Classic Finals. Bron Breakker collides with Robert Roode.

episodes.name: NXT #667
episodes.overview: Cameron Grimes, Roderick Strong and A-Kid vie for the final spot in the NXT North American Championship Ladder Match at NXT Stand & Deliver. Ivy Nile faces Tiffany Stratton. Bodhi Hayward represents Chase U when he takes on Von Wagner.

episodes.name: NXT #668 - NXT Stand & Deliver
episodes.overview: NXT 2.0's best and brightest Superstars converge on American Airlines Center in Dallas. Bron Breakker challenges Dolph Ziggler for the coveted NXT Championship. NXT Women's Champion Mandy Rose collides with Cora Jade, Io Shirai and Kay Lee Ray in a Fatal 4-Way Match. Carmelo Hayes puts his NXT North American Title on the line in a Ladder Match.

episodes.name: NXT #669
episodes.overview: Bron Breakker brings the NXT Championship back to NXT 2.0 after winning the title on Raw. Raquel Gonzalez & Dakota Kai put the NXT Women's Tag Team Championship on the line against Toxic Attraction. Nikkita Lyons clashes with Lash Legend. New North American Champion Cameron Grimes addresses his victory at NXT Stand & Deliver.

episodes.name: NXT #670
episodes.overview: Three huge title showdowns highlight a special championship edition of NXT 2.0. Mandy Rose defends her NXT Women's Championship against Dakota Kai. Cameron Grimes and Solo Sikoa clash for the NXT North American Championship. Five tag teams vie for the vacant NXT Tag Team Championship in a Gauntlet Match.

episodes.name: NXT #671
episodes.overview: New NXT Tag Team Champions Pretty Deadly begin their title reign. Carmelo Hayes battles Santos Escobar. Grayson Waller squares off against his former bodyguard Sanga. Newcomer Tatum Paxley takes on Natalya. Sarray looks to settle the score with Tiffany Stratton.

episodes.name: NXT #672
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Bron Breakker’s highly personal conflict with Joe Gacy heats up with NXT Spring Breakin' on the horizon. Nikkita Lyons and Lash Legend collide in a rematch. Solo Sikoa seeks retribution against Trick Williams.

episodes.name: NXT #673
episodes.overview: The NXT Title is on the line at NXT Spring Breakin' as Bron Breakker battles Joe Gacy. Cameron Grimes, Carmelo Hayes and Solo Sikoa clash for the NXT North American Title. Tony D'Angelo and Santos Escobar have a sit-down to settle their differences. Cora Jade & Nikkita Lyons join forces to face Lash Legend & Natalya.

episodes.name: NXT #674
episodes.overview: The first-ever NXT Women’s Breakout Tournament kicks off with two opening round matches. Cora Jade looks to prove she belongs in a one-on-one showdown with Natalya. Wendy Choo & Roxanne Perez challenge Toxic Attraction for the NXT Women's Tag Team Championship.

episodes.name: NXT #675
episodes.overview: Tony D’Angelo and Santos Escobar settle their score in the ring. The first-ever NXT Women's Breakout Tournament continues. The Creed Brothers collide with The Viking Raiders. Cameron Grimes & Solo Sikoa join forces to take on Carmelo Hayes & Trick Williams.

episodes.name: NXT #676
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Bron Breakker battles Duke Hudson. Indi Hartwell faces NXT Women's Champion Mandy Rose. Alba Fyre clashes with Elektra Lopez. Ikemen Jiro takes on the massive Von Wagner. The NXT Women's Breakout Tournament continues with two Semifinal Matches.

episodes.name: NXT #677
episodes.overview: North American Champion Cameron Grimes clashes with Nathan Frazer days ahead of his battle with Carmelo Hayes at NXT In Your House. Toxic Attraction sit down with Katana Chance & Kayden Carter for the Women’s Championship Summit. NXT Tag Team Champions Pretty Deadly take on Roderick Strong & Damon Kemp.

episodes.name: NXT #678 - NXT In Your House
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Bron Breakker must contain his rage as he battles Joe Gacy in a match where Breakker loses his title if he gets disqualified. The Creed Brothers challenge Pretty Deadly for the NXT Tag Team Championship. Cameron Grimes defends the NXT North American Title against former champion Carmelo Hayes.

episodes.name: NXT #679
episodes.overview: A returning Superstar answers NXT Champion Bron Breakker's open challenge. Carmelo Hayes celebrates his NXT North American Championship victory. Roxanne Perez and Tiffany Stratton battle in the Women's Breakout Tournament Final.

episodes.name: NXT #680
episodes.overview: Cora Jade, Roxanne Perez & Indi Hartwell clash with Toxic Attraction. NXT Champion Bron Breakker battles Duke Hudson. Edris Enofé & Malik Blade challenge NXT Tag Team Champions The Creed Brothers. Giovanni Vinci makes his NXT 2.0 debut against up-and-comer Guru Raaj.

episodes.name: NXT #681
episodes.overview: Tony D'Angelo challenges NXT North American Champion Carmelo Hayes. Solo Sikoa collides with Grayson Waller. Alba Fyre faces Lash Legend. Edris Enofé battles Cameron Grimes.

episodes.name: NXT #682
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Bron Breakker comes face-to-face with his Great American Bash challenger Cameron Grimes. Cora Jade & Roxanne Perez face Katana Chance & Kayden Carter for a chance to challenge for the NXT Women's Tag Team Championship. Ikemen Jiro clashes with Giovanni Vinci.

episodes.name: NXT #683
episodes.overview: Champions and challengers collide at The Great American Bash. NXT Champion Bron Breakker clashes with Cameron Grimes. Grayson Waller challenges Carmelo Hayes for the NXT North American Title. Toxic Attraction battle Roxanne Perez & Cora Jade for the NXT Women's Tag Titles. NXT Tag Champions The Creed Brothers face Roderick Strong & Damon Kemp.

episodes.name: NXT #684
episodes.overview: Roxanne Perez challenges Mandy Rose for the NXT Women's Title. Apollo Crews collides with Giovanni Vinci. Solo Sikoa battles Von Wagner.

episodes.name: NXT #685
episodes.overview: A 20-Woman Battle Royal determines the next challenger to NXT Women's Champion Mandy Rose. Josh Briggs & Brooks Jensen defend their NXT UK Tag Team Championship against Pretty Deadly. JD McDonagh battles Cameron Grimes. Roderick Strong faces Damon Kemp.

episodes.name: NXT #686
episodes.overview: Diamond Mine collide with Tony D’Angelo’s “Family” in an Eight-Man Tag Team Match. Zoey Stark addresses her road to recovery and future NXT Women's Title opportunity. Apollo Crew faces Xyon Quinn. Wes Lee battles Grayson Waller.

episodes.name: NXT #687
episodes.overview: Solo Sikoa and Von Wagner collide in Falls Count Anywhere Match. The vacant NXT Women’s Tag Team Titles are on the line in Fatal 4-Way Tag Team Match. NXT Tag Team Champions The Creed Brothers face Tony D'Angelo & "Stacks." Bron Breakker and JD McDonagh sit down for an NXT Heatwave Summit.

episodes.name: NXT #688
episodes.overview: Zoey Stark battles Cora Jade. Santos Escobar and Tony D’Angelo meet for a final one-on-one accord. Wes Lee throws down with Trick Williams in a Rounds Match. Nikkita Lyons faces Kiana James.

episodes.name: NXT #689
episodes.overview: Tensions boil over at NXT Heatwave as Bron Breakker puts his NXT Championship on the line against JD McDonagh. NXT Women's Champion Mandy Rose battles Zoey Stark. Giovanni Vinci challenges NXT North American Champion Carmelo Hayes. Santos Escobar and Tony D'Angelo clash for the fate of Legado del Fantasma.

episodes.name: NXT #690
episodes.overview: After his shocking arrival to NXT 2.0, NXT UK Champion Tyler Bate battles Von Wagner. The Gallus Boys challenge Josh Briggs & Brooks Jensen for the NXT UK Tag Team Championship. Wendy Choo faces Tiffany Stratton in a Lights Out Match. "The Grayson Waller Effect" debuts with guest Apollo Crews.

episodes.name: NXT #691
episodes.overview: The best of NXT and NXT UK set the stage for NXT Worlds Collide. Diamond Mine and Gallus go toe-to-toe in a massive Six-Man Tag Team Match. Zoey Stark looks to silence Kiana James. Apollo Crews gets his hands on Grayson Waller.

episodes.name: NXT #692 - Worlds Collide
episodes.overview: NXT 2.0 collides with NXT UK as the top Superstars from both brands battle in dream showdowns. NXT Champion Bron Breakker faces NXT UK Champion Tyler Bate in a Title vs. Title Match. NXT Women's Champion Mandy Rose, NXT UK Women's Champion Meiko Satomura and Blair Davenport clash in a Title Unification Triple Threat Match.

episodes.name: NXT #693
episodes.overview: Nathan Frazer and Axiom collide in the first match of their best-of-three series. Wes Lee faces JD McDonagh. Ricochet seeks payback against Trick Williams. Nikki A.S.H. & Doudrop clash with Toxic Attraction. Roxanne Perez battles Meiko Satomura.

episodes.name: NXT #694
episodes.overview: The WWE Universe celebrates the one-year anniversary of NXT 2.0. Pretty Deadly look to escape as they defend the NXT Tag Team Titles against The Creed Brothers in a Steel Cage Match. “The A Champ” Carmelo Hayes puts the NXT North American Title on the line against a mystery opponent.

episodes.name: NXT #695
episodes.overview: Tyler Bate and JD McDonagh battle for a future NXT Championship opportunity. Wendy Choo faces Cora Jade. Von Wagner collides with Sanga in a colossal showdown. Nathan Frazer squares off against Axiom in the second match of their best-of-three series.

episodes.name: NXT #696
episodes.overview: Josh Briggs & Brooks Jensen collide with Gallus in a Pub Rules Match. Mandy Rose faces Fallon Henley. Wes Lee battles Tony D’Angelo for a spot in the North American Title Ladder Match. Brutus Creed seeks retribution against Damon Kemp.

episodes.name: NXT #697
episodes.overview: A new NXT era begins. Alba Fyre, Nikkita Lyons & Zoey Stark join forces to battle Toxic Attraction. Grayson Waller welcomes Cora Jade and Roxanne Perez to “The Grayson Waller Effect.” NXT Tag Team Champions Pretty Deadly deliver an address of the NXT Commonwealth.

episodes.name: NXT #698
episodes.overview: Bron Breakker battles Javier Bernal. A Triple Threat Tag Team No. 1 Contenders’ Match determines Pretty Deadly’s next challengers. Axiom and Nathan Frazer clash in the third and final match of their best-of-three-series. Alba Fyre faces Jacy Jayne.

episodes.name: NXT #699
episodes.overview: Roxanne Perez and Cora Jade Pick Their Poison ahead of Halloween Havoc as Jade faces Raquel Rodriguez while Perez battles Rhea Ripley. Sonya Deville takes on Alba Fyre. Cameron Grimes enlists the help of Luke Gallows & Karl Anderson against The Schism in a Six-Man Tag Team Match. Oro Mensah & Wes Lee team up against Carmelo Hayes & Trick Williams.

episodes.name: NXT #700 - Halloween Havoc
episodes.overview: It’s trick or treat for the Superstars of NXT squaring off on a terrifying night filled with weapons, ladders and ambulances. Bron Breakker defends the NXT Championship against Ilja Dragunov and JD McDonagh. Six Superstars battle in a Ladder Match for the vacant NXT North American Championship.

episodes.name: NXT #701
episodes.overview: Nikkita Lyons & Zoey Stark challenge NXT Women's Tag Team Champions Kayden Carter & Katana Chance. NXT Tag Team Champions Pretty Deadly face Malik Blade & Edris Enofé. Schism reveal their mysterious fourth member. Shotzi takes on Lash Legend.

episodes.name: NXT #702
episodes.overview: Mandy Rose celebrates one year as NXT Women's Champion. NXT Champion Bron Breakker returns after a successful title defense at Halloween Havoc. Schism gives an interview following the addition of Ava Raine. R-Truth comes to NXT to face Grayson Waller. Odyssey Jones makes his NXT in-ring return.

episodes.name: NXT #703
episodes.overview: Katana Chance & Kayden Carter battle Zoey Stark & Nikkita Lyons in a rematch for the NXT Women's Tag Team Championship. NXT Champion Bron Breakker and Von Wagner join "The Grayson Waller Effect." Brutus Creed collides with Damon Kemp in a Five-Minute Challenge. Cameron Grimes looks to take down Joe Gacy and Schism.

episodes.name: NXT #704
episodes.overview: Bron Breakker defends the NXT Championship against Von Wagner. Mandy Rose faces Alba Fyre in an NXT Women's Title Last Woman Standing Match. Shawn Michaels makes a major announcement about NXT Deadline. Booker T hosts NXT North American Championship contract signing between Carmelo Hayes and Wes Lee.

episodes.name: NXT #705
episodes.overview: Carmelo Hayes attempts to become a three-time NXT North American Champion when he challenges Wes Lee for the prized title. NXT Women's Champion Mandy Rose and Toxic Attraction address the NXT Universe. Wendy Choo and Cora Jade clash after weeks of insults.

episodes.name: NXT #706
episodes.overview: Shawn Michaels calls on WWE Hall of Famers X-Pac, Road Dogg, Molly Holly and Alundra Blayze to help announce the competitors for the first-ever Iron Survivor Challenge Matches. Nikkita Lyons teams with NXT Women’s Tag Team Champions Kayden Carter & Katana Chance to battle Toxic Attraction. Dijak returns to NXT squared circle.

episodes.name: NXT #707
episodes.overview: Axiom, Von Wagner and Andre Chase battle it out for the final Men's Iron Survivor Challenge spot. Indi Hartwell, Wendy Choo and Fallon Henley compete for the final Women's Iron Survivor Challenge spot. The Men's Iron Survivor Challenge competitors join "The Grayson Waller Effect." Pretty Deadly present "A Real Christmas Story."

episodes.name: NXT #708 - Deadline
episodes.overview: NXT Superstars compete against each other and the clock in the first-ever Iron Survivor Challenges to determine the No. 1 contenders to the NXT Championship and NXT Women's Championship. Bron Breakker defends the NXT Title against Apollo Crews.

episodes.name: NXT #709
episodes.overview: After winning the Iron Survivor Challenge at NXT Deadline, Roxanne Perez challenges NXT Women's Champion Mandy Rose. The New Day come to NXT as the NXT Tag Team Champions. Ivy Nile & Tatum Paxley face Toxic Attraction. Lyra Valkyria makes her NXT debut. Odyssey Jones collides with Von Wagner in a colossal showdown.

episodes.name: NXT #710
episodes.overview: Josh Briggs & Brooks Jensen challenge NXT Tag Team Champions The New Day. Kayden Carter & Katana Chance defend the NXT Women's Tag Team Championship in a Triple Threat Match. Axiom faces Carmelo Hayes. Nikkita Lyons battles Zoey Stark.

episodes.name: NXT #711
episodes.overview: Wes Lee faces Tony D'Angelo in a North American Championship Match. Fallon Henley battles Kiana James for her family's bar. Malik Blade, Edris Enofé & Odyssey Jones clash with Schism. Cora Jade collides with Wendy Choo.

episodes.name: NXT #712
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Bron Breakker comes face-to-face with Grayson Waller on "The Grayson Waller Effect." Carmelo Hayes faces Apollo Crews. Alba Fyre takes on Isla Dawn in an Extreme Resolution Match. Axiom looks for retribution against Trick Williams.

episodes.name: NXT #713
episodes.overview: NXT New Year's Evil brings a big NXT Championship Match between Bron Breakker and Grayson Waller. Twenty women compete in a Battle Royal to determine the No. 1 Contender to the NXT Women's Championship. Tony D'Angelo defends his family's honor against Dijak.

episodes.name: NXT #714
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Bron Breakker and Grayson Waller address their upcoming Steel Cage Match at NXT Vengeance Day. Apollo Crews joins forces with Axiom to take on Carmelo Hayes & Trick Williams. Sol Ruca battles Alba Fyre. Josh Briggs & Brooks Jensen clash with Gallus.

episodes.name: NXT #715
episodes.overview: Roxanne Perez, Gigi Dolin, and Jacy Jayne participate in an NXT Women’s Championship Summit. Kayden Carter & Katana Chance defend the NXT Women’s Tag Team Championship against Alba Fyre. Wendy Choo faces Elektra Lopez. Indi Hartwell battles Tiffany Stratton.

episodes.name: NXT #716
episodes.overview: Andre Chase & Duke Hudson, Edris Enofé & Malik Blade, and The Dyad face off in The New Day Invitational. Roxanne Perez responds to Toxic Attraction's attack. Bron Breakker and Grayson Waller prepare for their NXT Championship Steel Cage Match at NXT Vengeance Day.

episodes.name: NXT #717 - Vengeance Day
episodes.overview: There’s nothing sweeter than Vengeance. Bron Breakker battles Grayson Waller in a Steel Cage Match for the NXT Championship. Roxanne Perez and Toxic Attraction's Gigi Dolin and Jacy Jayne collide in a Triple Threat Match for the NXT Women's Championship.

episodes.name: NXT #718
episodes.overview: Bayley returns to NXT to host her signature talk show, "Ding Dong, Hello!" with guests Toxic Attraction. Carmelo Hayes addresses his triumphant night at NXT Vengeance Day. Sol Ruca battles Zoey Stark. Lyra Valkyria takes on Valentina Feroz.

episodes.name: NXT #719
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Bron Breakker's return is met with a new challenger. NXT Women's Champion Roxanne Perez teams with Meiko Satomura to take on Kayden Carter & Katana Chance. Jacy Jayne explains why she attacked her Toxic Attraction cohort Gigi Dolin. Wes Lee issues an Open Challenge for the NXT North American Title.

episodes.name: NXT #720
episodes.overview: Bron Breakker battles Jinder Mahal for the NXT Championship. Andre Chase & Duke Hudson defend Thea Hail’s honor against The Dyad. Indi Hartwell faces Jacy Jayne. Edris Enofé & Malik Blade clash with NXT Tag Team Champions Gallus in non-title action.

episodes.name: NXT #721
episodes.overview: Tyler Bate collides with Carmelo Hayes. Gigi Dolin addresses the WWE Universe amid her conflict with Jacy Jayne. Wes Lee issues an Open Challenge for the NXT North American Title. Meiko Satomura battles Zoey Stark. Sol Ruca faces Elektra Lopez.

episodes.name: NXT #722
episodes.overview: Roxanne Perez defends the NXT Women's Championship against Meiko Satomura. Bron Breakker teams with The Creed Brothers to face Jinder Mahal & Indus Sher. Tony D'Angelo battles Dijak in a Jailhouse Street Fight. Former Toxic Attraction cohorts Gigi Dolin and Jacy Jayne collide.

episodes.name: NXT #723
episodes.overview: Bron Breakker and Carmelo Hayes sign the contract for their highly-anticipated NXT Championship Match at NXT Stand & Deliver. Gallus defend the NXT Tag Team Championship against Pretty Deadly. Johnny Gargano speaks ahead of his showdown against Grayson Waller.

episodes.name: NXT #724
episodes.overview: Indi Hartwell faces Tiffany Stratton, and Lyra Valkyria battles Ivy Nile in NXT Women's Championship Qualifying Matches. Ilja Dragunov clashes with JD McDonagh. Chase U meets Schism face-to-face in a Great Debate.

episodes.name: NXT #725
episodes.overview: Shawn Michaels decides NXT Women’s Champion Roxanne Perez's fate for NXT Stand & Deliver. Grayson Waller responds to Johnny Gargano's challenge of an Unsanctioned Match. Indi Hartwell, Sol Ruca and Ivy Nile clash in a Last Chance Qualifying Match for a spot in the NXT Women’s Title Ladder Match.

episodes.name: NXT 726 - Stand and Deliver
episodes.overview: Bron Breakker and Carmelo Hayes finally cross paths on NXT's biggest stage when they clash for the NXT Championship. Roxanne Perez defends her NXT Women's Championship in a Six-Woman Ladder Match. Johnny Gargano returns to NXT to take on Grayson Waller.

episodes.name: NXT #727
episodes.overview: New NXT Champion Carmelo Hayes kicks off the HIM era. Wes Lee defends the NXT North American Title against Axiom. Dragon Lee faces Nathan Frazer. Tony D’Angelo & Channing “Stacks” Lorenzo battle Pretty Deadly. Dijak collides with Odyssey Jones.

episodes.name: NXT #728
episodes.overview: A Fatal 4-Way Match determines the No. 1 Contender to NXT Champion Carmelo Hayes. Fallon Henley & Kiana James try to win back the NXT Women’s Tag Team Titles from Alba Fyre & Isla Dawn. Von Wagner must defeat Ilja Dragunov or Mr. Stone will terminate his services with Wagner. Sol Ruca takes on Tiffany Stratton.

episodes.name: NXT #729
episodes.overview: NXT Champion Carmelo Hayes appears on "The Grayson Waller Effect." NXT North American Champion Wes Lee clashes with Charlie Dempsey. Gallus defend the NXT Tag Team Titles in a Triple Threat Match against The Creed Brothers and The Dyad. Noam Dar returns to NXT. Roxanne Perez battles Zoey Stark.

episodes.name: NXT #730 - Sping Breakkin
episodes.overview: NXT Superstars go Spring Breakin' as Indi Hartwell defends her NXT Women's Championship against Roxanne Perez and Tiffany Stratton in a Triple Threat Match. Carmelo Hayes faces Grayson Waller for the NXT Championship. The Family faces Pretty Deadly in the first-ever Trunk Match.

episodes.name: NXT #731
episodes.overview: Isla Dawn & Alba Fyre defend the NXT Women's Tag Team Titles against Kayden Carter & Katana Chance. Dani Palmer makes her NXT debut. Drew Gulak challenges NXT North American Champion Wes Lee. JD McDonagh has one last match in NXT against Dragon Lee.

episodes.name: NXT #732
episodes.overview: Trick Williams takes on Bron Breakker. The NXT Women's Championship Tournament kicks off as Tiffany Stratton faces Gigi Dolin, and Kiana James battles Lyra Valkyria. Gallus defend the NXT Tag Team Titles against The Dyad. Ilja Dragunov clashes with Dijak.

episodes.name: NXT #733
episodes.overview: The NXT Women's Championship Tournament continues as Roxanne Perez takes on Jacy Jayne, and Fallon Henley battles Cora Jade. The Creed Brothers clash with The Dyad. Dragon Lee joins Noam Dar's "Supernova Sessions."

episodes.name: NXT #734
episodes.overview: Lyra Valkyria faces Cora Jade, and Roxanne Perez battles Tiffany Stratton in the semifinals of the NXT Women's Championship Tournament.

episodes.overview: Carmelo Hayes defends the NXT Championship against Bron Breakker in a highly-anticipated rematch. Lyra Valkyria faces Tiffany Stratton for the vacant NXT Women's Championship.

episodes.name: NXT #739

episodes.name: NXT #740

episodes.name: NXT #741

episodes.name: NXT #742
episodes.overview: Bron Breakker battles Ilja Dragunov in an NXT Championship No. 1 Contender's Match. The Judgment Day come to NXT.

episodes.name: NXT #743
episodes.overview: Wes Lee defends the NXT North American Championship against The Judgment Day's Dominik Mysterio. Tony D'Angelo receives an NXT Homecoming.

episodes.name: NXT #744
episodes.overview: Carmelo Hayes, Trick Williams and Ilja Dragunov take on Schism. Gable Stevenson makes an announcement about his in-ring future.

episodes.name: NXT #746
episodes.overview: The bitter rivalry for Lyra Valkyria and Jacy Jayne comes to a head. Andre Chase battles Baron Corbin.

episodes.name: NXT #747

episodes.name: NXT #748
episodes.overview: Wes Lee and Dijak go one-on-one for an NXT Title opportunity. Thea Hail and Jacy Jayne square off. Trick Williams collides with Drew Gulak.

episodes.overview: NXT Superstars feel the Heatwave when Carmelo Hayes defends his NXT Title against Wes Lee. Trick Williams collides with Ilja Dragunov.

episodes.name: NXT #750
episodes.overview: A Fatal 4-Way Match determines the No. 1 Contender for the NXT Women's Title. The Creed Brothers take on The Dyad inside a steel cage.

episodes.overview: NXT Superstars show No Mercy as NXT Women's Champion Becky Lynch collides with Tiffany Stratton in an Extreme Rules Match.

episodes.overview: Cody Rhodes makes a huge announcement. John Cena will back up Carmelo Hayes as he takes on Bron Breakker with Paul Heyman in his corner.

episodes.name: NXT #758
episodes.overview: A new challenger to Ilja Dragunov’s NXT Championship is decided in a Triple Threat Match between Carmelo Hayes, Baron Corbin and Dijak.

episodes.overview: NXT travels to Chicago for its CW premiere. Trick Williams challenges NXT Champion Ethan Page with Special Guest Referee CM Punk.

episodes.name: October 8th 2024
episodes.overview: Randy Orton returns to his hometown of St. Louis to battle Je'Von Evans. Tony D'Angelo challenges NXT North American Champion Oba Femi.

episodes.name: October 15th 2024
episodes.overview: Wes Lee, Je'Von Evans and Ethan Page compete in a No. 1 Contender's Triple Threat Match. Stephanie Vaquer makes her NXT in-ring debut.

episodes.name: October 22nd 2024
episodes.overview: Giulia & Stephanie Vaquer team up for the first time ever to take on Fatal Influence. Trick Williams and Ethan Page come face-to-face.

episodes.name: October 29th 2024
episodes.overview: The fallout from Halloween Havoc. Zaria makes her NXT in-ring debut. Lexis King challenges NXT Heritage Cup Champion Charlie Dempsey

episodes.name: November 6th, 2024
episodes.overview: NXT emanates from the former ECW Arena in Philadelphia. Trick Williams & WWE Hall of Famer Bubba Ray Dudley face Ethan Page & Ridge Holland.
